Bhagat Singh, Chandrashekhar Azad, Ashfaqulla Khan, Rajguru and Durga Bhabhi
Bhagat Singh, Chandrashekhar Azad,  Ashfaqulla Khan, Rajguru 還有Durga Bhabhi

