我是認真的

248
00:29:06,740 --> 00:29:09,830
The four of you will be perfect for the roles...
你們演Bhagat Singh, Chandrashekhar Azad, Ashfaqulla Khan, Rajguru非常合適

249
00:29:12,940 --> 00:29:14,740
And Sonia will be my Durga Bhabhi.
而Sonia就做我的Durga Bhabhi

250
00:29:15,110 --> 00:29:16,640
She really knows Hindi!
她真的懂印地語

251
00:29:17,680 --> 00:29:20,580
All this talk of patriotism is boring.
說這些愛國主義很無聊

252
00:29:20,780 --> 00:29:24,850
