飛了很久

288
00:32:08,080 --> 00:32:09,140
Everything Ok at college?
大學裏還好吧?

289
00:32:10,320 --> 00:32:10,950
Everything's fine Dad.
都好, 爸

290
00:32:11,160 --> 00:32:14,620
Have you decided which American university you want to go to next year?
等下, 想好明年去哪所美國大學沒?

291
00:32:16,230 --> 00:32:21,500
