00:36:12,710 --> 00:36:14,040
What lips...
嘴唇真性感..

349
00:36:14,540 --> 00:36:17,130
Learn the lines properly, we meet tomorrow.
好好看台詞, 我們明天見

350
00:36:17,740 --> 00:36:20,440
8 a.m. Sharp!
八點準時排演!

351
00:36:20,650 --> 00:36:21,370
Nine
九..

352
00:36:22,290 --> 00:36:23,850
Sharp at eight.
八點整!                        哦八點

353
00:36:23,880 --> 00:36:25,910
We've already wasted a day...
我們已經浪費一天了

354
00:36:31,690 --> 00:36:34,590
Aslam, your sister-in-law looks even better when she's angry.
Aslam, 你嫂子生氣時更好看了

355
00:36:45,500 --> 00:36:46,660
What are you doing Laxman?
在幹什麼呢, Laxman?

356
00:36:51,410 --> 00:36:54,200
Party High Command is really happy with your work.
黨高層對你的工作很滿意

357
00:36:54,710 --> 00:36:59,110
These demonstrations that you have started against Western culture...
你牴觸西方文化做的努力

358
00:36:59,520 --> 00:37:03,010
...they've helped us overshadow other parties.
令其它黨派相形見絀

359
00:37:13,670 --> 00:37:15,800
This is for you. And this is for your boys.
這是給你和你的朋友的

360
00:37:16,870 --> 00:37:18,590
It's not necessary, Mishraji.
沒有必要, Mishraji

361
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:20,990
I'm not doing this for money.
我是為了黨不是為了錢

362
00:37:21,470 --> 00:37:24,060
I really believe in the principles of my party.
我真的相信我黨的理念

363
00:37:25,010 --> 00:37:26,470
That's fine Laxman...
很好Laxman..

364
00:37:27,110 --> 00:37:33,020
...but every movement needs fuel... Keep it.
但每次行動也需要燃油.. 拿著

365
00:37:40,130 --> 00:37:41,180
March the 14th
3月14日

366
00:37:41,840 --> 00:37:43,090
We started the rehearsals
我們開始了排演

367
00:37:44,060 --> 00:37:47,130
To say I was nervous would be an understatement
說我是緊張遠遠不夠

368
00:37:55,170 --> 00:37:59,700
There is nothing you can do to break me.
沒有什麼能把我打倒

369
00:38:00,080 --> 00:38:02,670
"Because I have made pain my friend."
因為疼痛是我的朋友

370
00:38:03,310 --> 00:38:06,980
"...As I hold Death's fingers."
因為我緊握死亡的手指

371
00:38:19,430 --> 00:38:22,420
DJ idiot, don't spoil my concentration.
DJ傻瓜, 不要影響我集中注意力

372
00:38:22,740 --> 00:38:24,090
Please guy, be serious
大家認真點

373
00:38:26,800 --> 00:38:28,400
Look, Death's finger.
看啊, 死亡的手指..

374
00:38:31,940 --> 00:38:34,540
"I've committed my life to the freedom of this country.
我已把自己獻給了國家的自由

375
00:38:34,750 --> 00:38:38,550
...I know you want me to get married, but I have made freedom my bride..."
我知道你希望我成家, 但自由就是我的新娘

376
00:38:38,750 --> 00:38:41,220
"Your obedient son, Bhagat Singh."
你順從的兒子, Bhagat Singh

377
00:38:42,990 --> 00:38:45,740
Who talks like this for God's sake?
誰會這麼說? 你順從的兒子

378
00:38:45,760 --> 00:38:47,640
My bride is freedom...
自由是我新娘, 他有什麼問題?

379
00:38:47,860 --> 00:38:50,260
I think it's a good line for Sukhi...
我看這句台詞對Sukhi挺合適

380
00:38:50,460 --> 00:38:52,160
Since no girl is ever going to marry him...
反正也沒有女孩子會嫁給他

381
00:38:52,400 --> 00:38:54,760
Let freedom be his bride.
就讓自由作他的新娘吧

382
00:38:54,970 --> 00:38:57,400
Laugh bastards, laugh.
笑吧混蛋, 笑吧

383
00:39:21,690 --> 00:39:24,030
This is the sari round of the Miss Freedom contest.
看啊, 是"自由小姐"競選穿的紗麗

384
00:39:25,060 --> 00:39:27,620
Just thought it would help me get into the character.
這樣能讓我感受角色

385
00:39:33,440 --> 00:39:35,600
Look guys this isn't going to work.
這樣是不行的

386
00:39:36,110 --> 00:39:40,410
You have to work hard to bring out the characters.
你們要認真地感受角色

387
00:39:41,080 --> 00:39:44,710
Unless you emote from within...
只有用心表演..

388
00:39:44,950 --> 00:39:46,650
...you won't understand these characters.
你們才會理解這些角色

389
00:39:48,050 --> 00:39:51,420
Try... it will come from within you.
試一下.. 會從你們內心流露出來

390
00:39:53,330 --> 00:39:56,320
See, he's got a hold of his character already.
他已經抓住他的角色了

391
00:39:56,560 --> 00:39:59,500
You understood the character pretty fast.
你理解人物挺快的

392
00:39:59,750 --> 00:40:00,420
Would you stop it?
不要胡鬧了

393
00:40:01,040 --> 00:40:01,850
Just shut up and get out
住口一邊去

394
00:40:02,090 --> 00:40:04,940
See! Now you look like a revolutionary!
看哪! 你看起來也完全是個革命者

395
00:40:05,510 --> 00:40:08,560
Whatever you say Gulabo, you need me to create the mood.
Gulabo不管怎麼說, 你還需要我來創造情緒

396
00:40:09,440 --> 00:40:11,240
DJ watch it.
DJ你看看

397
00:40:11,780 --> 00:40:13,140
Now she's upset!
現在她沮喪了

398
00:40:20,450 --> 00:40:23,950
Those are the words of a 23 year old.
Bhagat Singh才23歲, 這是他說的話

399
00:40:24,420 --> 00:40:27,590
That's how old Bhagat Singh was when he died: 23.
這也是他犧牲的年齡

400
00:40:28,160 --> 00:40:29,790
Those were different times Sue.
那個時代不同

401
00:40:30,230 --> 00:40:35,430
Today, if you tell people that you want to give your life for your country...
現在, 你要是跟人說, 把生命獻給祖國

402
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:36,990
...they'll call you nuts.
他們會說你傻

403
00:40:38,270 --> 00:40:39,030
Exactly.
正是

404
00:40:40,540 --> 00:40:43,770
I don't think I can relate to this...
我覺得和我沒什麼共同點

405
00:40:45,710 --> 00:40:47,040
That's it. Don't think.
行了, 不要想了

406
00:40:47,580 --> 00:40:52,110
Feel. Just read the words, Feel them.
去感覺, 讀這些文字, 去感覺

407
00:40:53,620 --> 00:40:55,250
Why don't we try again?
何不再來一次?

408
00:40:55,820 --> 00:40:57,420
Let's try again...
再試一次

409
00:40:59,490 --> 00:41:02,350
I've committed my life to the freedom of this country.
我已把自己獻給了國家的自由

410
00:41:05,870 --> 00:41:11,170
...a job... a well settled life... these things don't matter anymore.
工作, 安定的生活, 都已經不再重要

411
00:41:12,010 --> 00:41:21,070
...I know you want me to get married, but I have made freedom my bride...
我知道你希望我成家, 但是自由就是我的新娘

412
00:41:32,930 --> 00:41:38,590
I swear on Mother India...
我, 印度母親的兒子, 在此莊嚴發誓..

413
00:41:52,380 --> 00:41:54,180
This Aslam is a real stud...
Aslam是個人物..

414
00:41:55,950 --> 00:42:01,250
Take a look at the packaging. Poetry, palmistry!
看看他的本事, 作詩, 相手..

415
00:42:02,220 --> 00:42:06,920
DJ, I'm scared at times that I'll remain a bachelor all my life.
DJ, 我有時怕會單身一輩子

416
00:42:08,530 --> 00:42:12,400
Trust me I won't let you die a bachelor.
相信我, 我不會讓你到死也是條單身漢

417
00:42:12,600 --> 00:42:13,230
Promise?
保證?

418
00:42:14,140 --> 00:42:15,130
It's DJ's promise.
這是DJ的保證

419
00:42:18,940 --> 00:42:24,540
You'll be writing people's destinies...
你會書寫人們的命運..

420
00:42:36,460 --> 00:42:38,220
Your love line is very strong...
你的愛情線很強

421
00:42:39,260 --> 00:42:42,930
The man of your dreams will come along in a black T-shirt and say:
你命中的男人會穿著黑T恤到來, 並說:

422
00:42:48,270 --> 00:42:51,610
Do I even have a love line?
我到底有沒有愛情線?

423
00:42:51,810 --> 00:42:53,570
You must have washed it off in the loo.
你一定在廁所裏洗掉了

424
00:42:53,780 --> 00:42:59,270
"Defence Minister Shastri has also been implicated in the MIG-21 kickbacks scandal,"
'國防部長Shastri也牽涉到MIG-21佣金醜聞'

425
00:42:59,480 --> 00:43:03,420
This is really depressing.
真教人鬱悶

426
00:43:03,620 --> 00:43:06,650
"This is a blatant lie. I am ordering an investigation."
'這是無恥的謊言, 我要求對此調查"

427
00:44:44,460 --> 00:44:45,580
See you guys.
再見夥計

428
00:44:46,360 --> 00:44:49,520
You're my buddy... I'll drop you home.
你是我夥計, 我送你回家

429
00:44:49,730 --> 00:44:52,630
I don't need any help, it's just two lanes away.
我不需要幫助, 才兩條街

430
00:44:53,270 --> 00:44:56,700
We aren't so drunk... that we've forgotten where you live.
我們沒醉到, 連你家都不記得在哪

431
00:45:10,020 --> 00:45:11,180
Idiots!
一幫傻瓜

432
00:45:12,920 --> 00:45:14,680
You're very lucky to have friends like them.
你有這樣的朋友很幸運

433
00:45:20,730 --> 00:45:23,200
One day this will all end.
有一天都會結束的

434
00:45:24,400 --> 00:45:26,200
We'll all go our separate ways.
我們會走上不同的路

435
00:45:27,300 --> 00:45:29,860
But you can always keep in touch.
但是你們可以保持聯繫

436
00:45:30,800 --> 00:45:31,960
Doesn't happen.
不會的

437
00:45:33,170 --> 00:45:34,730
Life gets busy.
生活會變得繁忙

438
00:45:35,510 --> 00:45:38,710
Too many problems. Getting a job, a house, money.
各種問題, 找工作, 房子, 賺錢

439
00:45:48,960 --> 00:45:52,390
In college we are the masters of our destinies...
在學校我們是命運的主人

440
00:45:53,190 --> 00:45:55,390
But after college we have to dance to fate's tune.
畢業後我們是命運的奴僕

441
00:46:02,200 --> 00:46:07,840
You know Gulabo. I passed out 5 years ago...
知道嗎Gulabo, 我5年前就畢業了

442
00:46:08,980 --> 00:46:10,500
...but I still hang around...
但我還在混..

443
00:46:10,950 --> 00:46:13,000
I don't understand.
我不明白

444
00:46:14,220 --> 00:46:17,280
...I don't ever want to leave college.
我一直不想離開學校

445
00:46:18,350 --> 00:46:19,130
Why?
為什麼?

446
00:46:21,560 --> 00:46:25,960
At least in the campus I'm someone... people know me.
起碼在學校人們認識我

447
00:46:27,130 --> 00:46:28,990
DJ's somebody...
DJ是個人物..

448
00:46:31,370 --> 00:46:36,390
People expect me to do something big in life.
人們對我抱有期望

449
00:46:38,840 --> 00:46:42,070
But when I'm out on the streets...
但是等我出來了

450
00:46:42,980 --> 00:46:48,140
I'll just be like the rest of the slobs in this country.
我不過就像國家的那些懶漢

451
00:46:59,000 --> 00:47:01,090
Nameless. Faceless. Scared. Just walking the streets...
什麼也不是, 又怕

452
00:47:02,030 --> 00:47:05,560
It's the beer... Everything came out.
喝了點酒, 把什麼都說了

453
00:47:09,670 --> 00:47:13,230
You know what else I'm scared of?
你知道我還怕什麼?

454
00:47:14,940 --> 00:47:16,540
Acting in your film.
在你的電影裏表演

455
00:47:18,210 --> 00:47:20,770
Don't worry... you're in safe hands.
別擔心, 有可靠的人保護

456
00:47:42,399 --> 00:47:43,339
Where have you been?
去哪了?

457
00:47:44,969 --> 00:47:45,869
Hello Uncle... How are you?
你好大伯

458
00:47:51,149 --> 00:47:55,409
We'll catch up tomorrow Aslam...
我們明天見Aslam

459
00:48:02,859 --> 00:48:03,659
You've been drinking?
你喝酒了?

460
00:48:04,789 --> 00:48:07,989
Dad, you know I don't drink.
爸, 你知道我不喝酒

461
00:48:08,429 --> 00:48:11,799
Good-for-nothings... Whatever, they're my friends.
他們一無是處                     不管怎樣他們是我朋友

462
00:48:11,999 --> 00:48:15,729
Friends! They feel no shame standing in front of...
什麼朋友! 他們不感到害臊..

463
00:48:15,939 --> 00:48:18,699
...yourfather with alcohol on their breath.
滿口酒氣站在你爸面前

464
00:48:19,039 --> 00:48:21,739
Why can't you get friends in your own community?
你怎麼不在我們的圈子裏找朋友?

465
00:48:22,449 --> 00:48:25,879
Why do you make friends with people who corrupt you, disgrace your religion...
為什麼跟這些讓你敗壞, 污辱信仰的人?

466
00:48:26,079 --> 00:48:27,779
This has nothing to do with religion, Father.
這跟信仰無關, 爸

467
00:48:27,989 --> 00:48:28,919
Shut up!
閉嘴!

468
00:48:30,629 --> 00:48:32,719
Don't raise your voice in the presence of yourfather.
跟你父親說話小心點

469
00:48:34,259 --> 00:48:35,189
He's right.
他說得對

470
00:48:36,959 --> 00:48:42,559
This country has never accepted Muslims and it never will...
這個國家從不接受穆斯林, 也絕不會

471
00:48:43,129 --> 00:48:44,569
How can you be so passive!
你怎能這麼漠視?

472
00:48:46,199 --> 00:48:49,139
Do you ever see me mixing with a Hindu?
你看見我跟印度教人混一起過嗎?

473
00:48:50,039 --> 00:48:53,939
I'm not you and I don't want to be like you brother.
我不是你, 你也不像你一樣

474
00:48:55,679 --> 00:48:57,149
I can't fill myself with so much hate...
我不能讓自己滿是仇恨

475
00:48:57,979 --> 00:49:00,209
Coward that's what you are.
膽小鬼你這點是改不了的

476
00:49:00,419 --> 00:49:02,079
Stop it!
不要說了

477
00:49:02,289 --> 00:49:05,309
I feel suffocated in this house. It's the same old thing every single day...
我在這裏受夠了, 每天都是同樣的爭吵

478
00:49:17,299 --> 00:49:20,329
Carnivals will be held on our graves every year,
我們的墓地每年都會有狂歡

479
00:49:21,109 --> 00:49:25,099
That's all that will be left of us, when we die for our country.
我們為國家死後, 留下的就是這個

480
00:49:25,309 --> 00:49:28,109
Well said Ashfaq Sahab...
說得好Ashfaq Sahab..

481
00:49:28,609 --> 00:49:30,949
If the English could hear you they would leave this country in a moment.
英國人要是聽見, 馬上會離開

482
00:49:33,319 --> 00:49:34,439
So what has been decided?
有什麼決定?

483
00:49:35,449 --> 00:49:41,519
We'll steal the Empire's money from the train that passes Kakori.
有一輛火車經過Kakori, 我們在那偷帝國的錢

484
00:49:42,489 --> 00:49:44,459
And with that money we will buy arms.
我們用那些錢來買武器

485
00:49:45,529 --> 00:49:47,729
Bismil will explain everything.
Bismil會仔細解釋

486
00:49:47,929 --> 00:49:50,699
Yes Bismil... Where is my Ram?
是Bismil.. 我的Ram在哪?

487
00:49:53,539 --> 00:49:55,699
I just can't find my Ramprasad Bismil.
我還是找不到我的Ramprasad Bismil

488
00:49:55,909 --> 00:49:57,379
Relax. We will find him.
放鬆, 會找到的

489
00:49:57,579 --> 00:49:59,169
But where? How?
在哪? 怎麼找?

490
00:49:59,479 --> 00:50:01,539
Very soon. Don't you wo...
很快, 你不是..

491
00:50:04,019 --> 00:50:06,209
You won't get Ramprasad Bismil out here.
你們在這是不會找到Ramprasad Bismil的

492
00:50:07,449 --> 00:50:09,549
You need a true Indian.
你們需要一個真正的印度人

493
00:50:10,489 --> 00:50:12,459
How can you find Indian revolutionaries amongst...
你在一群想成為西方人的人裏..

494
00:50:13,229 --> 00:50:15,859
...people who want to be Westerners?
怎麼找得到印度的革命家?

495
00:50:16,059 --> 00:50:17,499
Ignore him. Let's go.
別聽他說, 我們走

496
00:50:17,699 --> 00:50:21,029
Ramprasad Bismil wished to be reborn a hundred times...
Ramprasad Bismil希望重生100次..

497
00:50:23,139 --> 00:50:26,329
...so that he could give his life for his country a hundred times over.
以此為他的祖國獻身100次

498
00:50:26,539 --> 00:50:27,769
Let's go Sue.
我們走Sue

499
00:50:29,009 --> 00:50:32,669
So where do you think I can find my Bismil?
那在哪才能找到我的Bismil?

500
00:50:38,419 --> 00:50:39,579
I don't believe this.
真不敢相信

501
00:50:42,719 --> 00:50:47,719
This day, we walk along with death, and laugh at its pale spectre.
這一天我們與死亡同行, 嘲笑它蒼白的臉龐

502
00:50:48,929 --> 00:50:54,529
We will not fear those cruel swords, our courage is far sharper.
我們不懼怕殘忍尖刀, 我們的勇氣更為鋒利

503
00:50:55,339 --> 00:51:03,679
Mistake not our silence for submission. For beneath lies lava, molten.
不要錯把沉默當成屈服, 後面是那滾滾熔岩

504
00:51:06,379 --> 00:51:15,849
O Martyre, O men of valour. One day the enemy will sing your praises.
哦烈士, 哦英勇的人 有一天敵人也會讚頌你

505
00:51:16,759 --> 00:51:20,989
We will show our mettle when the moment of truth arrives...
當真理來臨, 我們會顯示勇氣

506
00:51:21,199 --> 00:51:26,499
...for courage lives in deeds, not boastful lies.
因為勇氣是行動, 而不是誇誇其談

507
00:51:26,999 --> 00:51:30,659
We've gathered in the enemy's lair, my friend...
我們聚集在敵人的巢穴, 朋友們..

508
00:51:30,869 --> 00:51:34,739
In the hope of dying for our motherland.
渴望為了祖國獻出生命

509
00:51:34,939 --> 00:51:39,569
We will not fearthose cruel swords, our courage is far sharper.
我們不懼怕殘忍尖刀, 我們的勇氣更為鋒利

510
