01:10:41,769 --> 01:10:45,569
You have a right to fight and die for it too...
你也有權利為她戰鬥和死亡

667
01:10:47,649 --> 01:10:48,909
...Forgive me.
原諒我

668
01:10:49,119 --> 01:10:50,739
Ram, let us not talk of dying...
Ram, 我們不要說死..

669
01:10:51,119 --> 01:10:56,419
I pray, that we all live to see our grandchildren grow up in a free country.
我祈禱, 我們都能看到孫兒生活在印度自由的土地上

670
01:11:00,959 --> 01:11:02,089
Ram run!
Ram, 跑!

671
01:12:17,699 --> 01:12:19,499
Where are your other friends?
你的同夥在哪?

672
01:12:20,369 --> 01:12:21,839
Where's Azad?
Azad在哪?

673
01:12:26,299 --> 01:12:28,549
Azad was not a man to be found easily
Azad不是輕易能找得到的

674
01:12:30,889 --> 01:12:32,349
A master of disguises
一個偽裝的高手

675
01:12:33,269 --> 01:12:34,579
They appeared and vanished at will
他們來去自由

676
01:12:36,379 --> 01:12:37,969
After months of frustration
幾個月的徒勞後

677
01:12:38,899 --> 01:12:40,709
The breakthrough came for the British goverment
不列顛政府找到了突破點

678
01:12:41,719 --> 01:12:45,549
Banwari, weakest revolutionary in captivity
Banwari, 囚禁下最弱的革命者

679
01:12:46,509 --> 01:12:49,959
A man who had given us to whereabouts for Bismil and Ashfaqullah
給了我們Bismil和Ashfaqullah下落的人

680
01:12:50,459 --> 01:12:52,579
agreed to be the bait to trap Azad
同意作餌引Azad上勾

681
01:12:54,629 --> 01:12:55,969
We had found our Judas
我們找到了我們的猶大

682
01:13:11,259 --> 01:13:12,059
Banwari!
Banwari

683
01:14:25,299 --> 01:14:26,819
I loved those songs and dances
歌舞真讓人叫絕

684
01:14:27,069 --> 01:14:29,389
Do they happen in your films? That's the reason we grow trees in this country...
你們電影裏有嗎? 這是我們種樹的原因..

685
01:14:29,399 --> 01:14:30,789
to dance around them.
圍著它們跳舞

686
01:14:36,649 --> 01:14:39,119
So where are we going?
我們去哪?

687
01:14:41,989 --> 01:14:43,499
Special day, special place!
特別的一天, 特別的地點

688
01:14:43,749 --> 01:14:44,519
Special DAY?
特別的一天?

689
01:15:56,889 --> 01:15:57,619
It's amazing
讓人驚嘆

690
01:16:00,399 --> 01:16:04,359
Ever since I was a kid I used to come here...
我還是小孩子的時候, 就經常來這

691
01:16:05,609 --> 01:16:10,369
...to watch planes take off... and watch them till they don't disappear in the sky.
看飛機起飛, 直到消失在天際

692
01:16:14,579 --> 01:16:16,549
What the hell are they doing?
他們是在幹嗎?

693
01:16:43,109 --> 01:16:44,369
I don't believe them.
真是難以相信

694
01:16:44,509 --> 01:16:45,069
Men!
男孩子!

695
01:16:45,609 --> 01:16:47,909
Come on, face it, you'd love to do that really.
得了, 接受吧, 你也很想那麼做

696
01:16:47,979 --> 01:16:50,379
What? Take my shirt off and howl at planes.
什麼? 脫掉衣服朝天空大叫?

697
01:16:50,619 --> 01:16:52,419
I won't mind if you do.
你要是這樣我不介意

698
01:16:52,949 --> 01:16:54,579
Dream on buddy...
你就做夢吧

699
01:17:03,459 --> 01:17:06,429
Boys and girls and Sukhi...
男孩, 女孩, 還有女孩的跟屁蟲Sukhi..

700
01:17:06,629 --> 01:17:07,759
Why me all the time?
怎麼老是我?

701
01:17:07,999 --> 01:17:09,439
I want to make a special announcement...
我有一個特別的聲明

702
01:17:10,969 --> 01:17:14,929
I was wondering if you'd like to spend the rest of your life with me...
我在想你願不願意跟我共度餘生

703
01:17:15,809 --> 01:17:19,769
...that's in case you aren't doing anything important...
要是你沒什麼重要事情的話?

704
01:17:23,889 --> 01:17:25,439
Will you please marry me?
你能嫁給我嗎?

705
01:18:13,339 --> 01:18:27,329
Without saying a word, you steal my heart.
"不要言語, 帶我同行"

706
01:18:28,219 --> 01:18:43,029
I'll find happiness by your side I can't stay apart
"哪有你的微笑, 就是我的終點"

707
01:18:45,399 --> 01:18:59,099
My life tastes sweet now,
"這幸福, 終於領悟"

708
01:19:00,209 --> 01:19:15,469
since you walked through that door.
"從此這生活, 變得甜如蜜"

709
01:19:16,369 --> 01:19:31,229
When your arms wrap around me, I know I've found my shore.
"你懷抱的海岸, 我的船終停靠"

710
01:19:33,449 --> 01:19:47,419
Without saying a word, you steal my heart.
"不要言語, 帶我同行"

711
01:20:17,029 --> 01:20:31,129
Sweep through the streets of my mind like a gentle spring.
"入我心途, 好似那朦朧雨"

712
01:20:33,009 --> 01:20:46,749
Walk through the corridors of my heart, fill the caravan of my dreams.
"夢想的旅行, 有了你的身影"

713
01:20:47,889 --> 01:21:03,239
I sway to the song of your soul.
"你哼的曲調, 成了我的旋律"

714
01:21:05,069 --> 01:21:19,509
Without saying a word, you steal my heart.
"不要言語, 帶我同行"

715
01:21:20,049 --> 01:21:35,199
I'll find happiness by your side, I can't stay apart.
"哪有你的微笑, 就是我的終點"

716
01:21:42,399 --> 01:21:44,299
The first thing that hit me about this man
這人第一次給我印象的

717
01:21:45,489 --> 01:21:46,169
was his voice
是他的聲音

718
01:21:49,689 --> 01:21:50,209
I knew then
然後我清楚

719
01:21:51,329 --> 01:21:52,979
My job was not going to be easy
這不會是件輕鬆活

720
01:21:53,659 --> 01:21:55,689
I'll come back later.
我過會再來

721
01:21:55,899 --> 01:21:57,469
My prayers won't stop
我的祈禱不會停止

722
01:21:58,579 --> 01:22:00,729
till my country gets its freedom.
直到我的祖國獲得自由

723
01:22:03,169 --> 01:22:05,699
I don't think you can wait till then.
我看你不能等到那個時候

724
01:22:07,169 --> 01:22:12,239
My name is James McKinley. I'm here to find out from you...
我名字是James McKinley, 我來這找出..

725
01:22:13,009 --> 01:22:16,639
...where Azad and the other terrorists are hiding.
Azad和其它恐怖分子躲在哪裏

726
01:22:16,849 --> 01:22:23,919
Not terrorists. Revolutionaries.
不是恐怖分子, 是革命者

727
01:22:34,879 --> 01:22:35,589
Breaking a man
拷問一個人

728
01:22:36,819 --> 01:22:37,749
Bit by bit
一點一點

729
01:22:39,609 --> 01:22:41,519
They said it will get easy with time
他們說會隨時間而習慣

730
01:22:43,849 --> 01:22:44,649
It never did
卻從來沒有

731
01:23:19,899 --> 01:23:21,339
The torture went on for some time
酷刑持續了一段時間

732
01:23:23,269 --> 01:23:24,609
But Bismil didn't break
Bismil沒有開口

733
01:23:30,519 --> 01:23:32,659
Both men have pain their friend
兩個人都忍受痛苦

734
01:23:34,099 --> 01:23:34,869
They didn't break
他們沒有招認

735
01:23:36,709 --> 01:23:37,399
Instead
反而

736
01:23:38,729 --> 01:23:41,649
They did something I've never seen any prisoner do before
他們做了我從沒見過別的囚犯做的事

737
01:23:49,209 --> 01:23:56,239
On this day, we walk with death and laugh at its pale spectre.
這一天我們與死亡同行, 嘲笑它蒼白的臉龐

738
01:23:57,649 --> 01:24:06,249
Death cannot take you Ashfaq, when you live in people's hearts and minds.
死亡不能壓垮你Ashfaq, 你活在人民的心中

739
01:24:07,989 --> 01:24:10,919
I think it was the poetry, that held their soul together
我想是詩歌把他們連繫在一起

740
01:24:11,659 --> 01:24:14,059
As the torture tore their body apart
當酷刑把他們的身體撕裂

741
01:24:16,719 --> 01:24:18,239
The torture didn't work
酷刑沒有奏效

742
01:24:19,569 --> 01:24:20,829
So we thought of other ways
於是我們想的別的辦法

743
01:24:21,309 --> 01:24:24,039
This is the Holy Quran.
孩子, 這是聖可蘭經

744
01:24:25,639 --> 01:24:30,269
Hindus like Bismil will create a country for themselves.
像Bismil這樣的印度教徒在創造他們自己的國家

745
01:24:30,479 --> 01:24:32,949
What will a Muslim like you get out of it? They're just using you.
穆斯林沒好處而是被利用

746
01:24:34,319 --> 01:24:37,849
He's not fighting for Hindu freedom, he's fighting for Hindustan's freedom.
他不是為印度教而戰, 是為印度自由而戰

747
01:24:39,319 --> 01:24:42,119
But you won't be able to understand this.
但是, 你是不會明白的

748
01:24:42,999 --> 01:24:46,449
You've been a slave so long you've begun to like it.
你做奴隸太久甚至都開始喜歡了

749
01:24:51,669 --> 01:24:54,399
Tell us where Azad and the other terrorists are...
說出Azad和其它恐怖分子的藏身處

750
01:24:55,839 --> 01:24:58,539
...You can still save yourself.
你們還能保住性命

751
01:25:08,019 --> 01:25:09,319
19 December.
12月19號(全印非婆羅門結盟達成)

752
01:25:10,019 --> 01:25:12,419
It's not yourfault...
這不是你的錯, McKinley先生

753
01:25:13,189 --> 01:25:15,659
...you're only doing your duty.
你只是在履行職責

754
01:25:15,399 --> 01:25:16,539
How can this be real?
這怎麼能真的發生?

755
01:25:20,039 --> 01:25:20,679
Tell me
告訴我

756
01:25:24,249 --> 01:25:25,199
Tell me
告訴我!

757
01:25:29,109 --> 01:25:30,899
How can this be the way of God
這怎麼會是神的道路?

758
01:25:45,019 --> 01:25:47,299
Please look after the one, they'll arrive at your door
請照顧這些會到你門口的人

759
01:25:51,469 --> 01:25:52,299
Oh my God
哦, 上帝

760
01:25:54,649 --> 01:25:56,659
I'm utterly sorry I've vanity
非常抱歉我還有虛榮..

761
01:27:08,399 --> 01:27:09,069
Hey guys, what's up?
夥計們, 怎麼樣?

762
01:27:14,939 --> 01:27:16,129
Whats wrong? Did someone die?
有人死了嗎?

763
01:27:18,439 --> 01:27:22,349
Sue... I haven't seen these guys so serious.
Sue, 我從沒見他們這麼嚴肅

764
01:27:23,279 --> 01:27:25,009
What are you doing to my friends?
你對他們做了什麼?

765
01:27:25,619 --> 01:27:30,579
It's not me... it's them. They've really begun to get into this.
沒什麼, 是他們.. 開始融入角色了

766
01:27:31,619 --> 01:27:33,819
Hey Laxman, aren't you coming along?
Laxman, 不一起去嗎?

767
01:27:34,289 --> 01:27:35,589
No. Some othertime.
不, 下次吧

768
01:27:35,789 --> 01:27:37,259
Come on. It's my last night in town.
來吧, 是我在這的最後一晚了

769
01:27:38,299 --> 01:27:39,759
I'm not really hungry.
不, 我很餓

770
01:27:39,969 --> 01:27:43,089
Watch us eat then. Come on.
看我們吃, 走吧

771
01:27:44,969 --> 01:27:46,769
Come on...
走吧..

772
01:27:59,319 --> 01:28:07,949
To two lovebirds with the most insanely romantic engagement in the whole wide world...
為Sonia和Ajay, 敬兩人訂婚, 祝激情浪漫到永遠

773
01:28:14,669 --> 01:28:17,069
I'm insane only about two things in my life.
我一生只為兩樣瘋狂

774
01:28:17,329 --> 01:28:20,529
Sonia and flying.
一個是飛行, 一個是Sonia

775
01:28:28,509 --> 01:28:33,309
You're lucky to feel so passionately about something.
你很幸福, 能對什麼充滿熱情

776
01:28:34,019 --> 01:28:35,649
You have your poetry Aslam.
你有你的詩歌啊

777
01:28:36,349 --> 01:28:38,149
Just like DJ has his singing.
就像DJ有他的歌唱

778
01:28:39,019 --> 01:28:41,649
Everyone has passion for something inside them, they just have to find this 'thing'.
每人都有熱情, 只需找到是什麼

779
01:28:42,189 --> 01:28:43,819
Just like our revolutionaries...
就像我們的革命者

780
01:28:44,029 --> 01:28:47,489
...their passion for freedom was greater than their love for their own lives.
他們對自由的熱忱超過了自身

781
01:28:47,699 --> 01:28:52,699
There's nothing in this world worth giving your life for. Nothing!
這世界沒什麼值得付出生命, 沒有

782
01:28:52,779 --> 01:28:53,309
Correct
正確

783
01:28:57,539 --> 01:28:59,099
Repeat.
重新來

784
01:28:59,309 --> 01:29:00,329
Easy DJ...
悠著點, 喝很多了

785
01:29:00,539 --> 01:29:01,909
Yes mama.
好, "媽媽"

786
01:29:03,709 --> 01:29:05,679
There are things worth giving your life for Karan.
有值得付出生命的東西

787
01:29:05,879 --> 01:29:07,349
Please.
說說看

788
01:29:07,719 --> 01:29:10,519
Bhagat Singh, Azad, Bismil, Ashfaq.. Like what?
Look at Bhagat Singh and Azad and the rest of those guys.

789
01:29:10,719 --> 01:29:12,689
They gave their lives for this country.
他們為了國家獻身

790
01:29:13,059 --> 01:29:15,459
Look what happened. All for nothing.
結果呢? 白死了

791
01:29:16,389 --> 01:29:20,189
It's a shit-hole today.
到現在也是個爛攤子, 又有誰在意?

792
01:29:22,069 --> 01:29:23,029
I give a shit.
我在意

793
01:29:23,569 --> 01:29:27,369
People like Ajay who fight for their country give a shit.
像Ajay這樣為國家奉獻的人在意

794
01:29:27,569 --> 01:29:29,939
So that people like you can sleep peacefully.
所以你們才能睡得安穩

795
01:29:31,739 --> 01:29:34,369
Sonia get real.
Sonia, 別感情用事, 現實點

796
01:29:34,579 --> 01:29:35,549
Sonia's right.
Sonia說得對

797
01:29:35,749 --> 01:29:39,709
Sue, it's all-fine for a foreigner like you to say all this...
Sue, 你是外國人說說還行

798
01:29:39,919 --> 01:29:43,379
Out here we're fighting for basics.
可在這, 人民還在為生存根本奮鬥

799
01:29:43,589 --> 01:29:46,389
...food, clothing and shelter.
食物, 衣服, 房屋

800
01:29:46,589 --> 01:29:50,219
Out here you try to change things you'll get even more screwed.
在這你要想改變什麼, 只會變得更糟

801
01:29:50,759 --> 01:29:53,389
Corruption is in our DNA.
腐敗簡直就刻在我們的基因裏

802
01:29:54,769 --> 01:29:56,389
There is no future for this country.
這個國家沒有未來

803
01:29:56,599 --> 01:30:00,969
She's talking about the past, you're thinking about the future...
她在講過去, 你卻想未來

804
01:30:01,269 --> 01:30:03,569
One leg in the past and one leg in the future,
一隻腳在過去, 一隻腳在未來

805
01:30:03,769 --> 01:30:05,399
that's why we're pissing on the present...
所以我們在現在"尿尿"

806
01:30:06,329 --> 01:30:07,189
DJ, you just shut up
DJ, 你閉嘴!

807
01:30:07,939 --> 01:30:09,499
For once in life get serious.
起碼認真一次

808
01:30:14,119 --> 01:30:18,919
Karan, it's easy to sit on the outside and be a critic...
Karan, 置身事外評論很簡單..

809
01:30:20,119 --> 01:30:22,179
...blaming others is even easier.
責怪他人更加簡單

810
01:30:23,959 --> 01:30:27,419
Why don't you go out there and change things?
你們怎麼不出去改變這一切?

811
01:30:27,629 --> 01:30:28,599
Take a stand.
勇敢站起來

812
01:30:29,629 --> 01:30:33,759
Join politics, the police force, government and clean it up.
加入政界, 警局, 政府, 清理社會

813
01:30:34,799 --> 01:30:37,209
But you won't! I'll tell you why...
可你們不會! 我告訴你們為什麼

814
01:30:38,479 --> 01:30:41,089
Because that takes hard work
因為那要付出相當的努力

815
01:30:45,229 --> 01:30:47,069
It's easier to crib.
抱怨要容易得多

816
01:30:48,749 --> 01:30:49,879
Nothing's going to change.
什麼也不會變的

817
01:30:50,419 --> 01:30:54,549
You can go to your grave trying... it won't make any difference.
你可以拚死嘗試, 但不會有什麼不同

818
01:30:54,759 --> 01:30:59,719
Correct... the only difference will be how you go to your grave...
對.. 唯一的不同是怎麼死

819
01:31:00,149 --> 01:31:00,859
DJ relax
DJ 悠著點

820
01:31:03,999 --> 01:31:09,129
I'm not drunk. Am I drunk Sue?
我沒有醉, 我醉了嗎, Sue?

821
01:31:11,669 --> 01:31:15,579
See, the director's word is final. Cut it!
看, 導演說了算. Cut

822
01:31:18,509 --> 01:31:21,479
Where were we?
說到哪了?

823
01:31:22,199 --> 01:31:23,299
The end up style
死法

824
01:31:27,119 --> 01:31:30,119
On the way to our graves.
死後怎樣去墳場

825
01:31:30,929 --> 01:31:34,359
We'll all be wrapped in white shrouds when we die.
我們死了都會包在裹屍布裏

826
01:31:35,469 --> 01:31:38,459
Only Ajay will be wrapped in the national flag.
只有Ajay包在國旗裏

827
01:31:38,669 --> 01:31:39,289
DJ stop it
DJ, 說夠了

828
01:31:40,239 --> 01:31:43,299
Karan, you can say whateveryou want,
Karan, 隨你怎麼說

829
01:31:44,039 --> 01:31:47,069
not even the street dogs will bark when we die.
我們死了連街上的狗都不會叫

830
01:31:48,849 --> 01:31:54,649
But Ajay will get a 21 gun salute.
但Ajay會有21聲鳴槍致敬

831
01:32:32,819 --> 01:32:34,879
Karan, this is for you.
Karan, 給你的

832
01:32:35,119 --> 01:32:36,749
For me? Thanks dude.
給我的? 謝謝

833
01:32:37,359 --> 01:32:39,259
The girls fall for him anyway...
反正女孩子不管怎樣都喜歡他

834
01:32:39,459 --> 01:32:40,949
If anyone deserves the jacket, it's me.
夾克要給人的話, 也該給我

835
01:32:40,959 --> 01:32:45,699
Wow! What a dutiful daughter-in-law.
哇! 大嬸, 多孝順的媳婦

836
01:32:46,069 --> 01:32:48,829
Come on, touch your fiance's feet.
來吧, 摸未婚夫的腳

837
01:32:49,939 --> 01:32:52,169
DJ's right. Touch my feet, madam.
DJ說得對, 來吧

838
01:32:55,409 --> 01:32:59,069
See what women in this country have to put up with?
看到了, 我國的婦女要忍受多少規矩

839
01:32:59,279 --> 01:33:03,219
I think DJ's right. You should respect your traditions.
我覺得DJ說得對, 你該遵守你的傳統

840
01:33:03,419 --> 01:33:04,679
See, even Sue agrees...
看, 連Sue也同意..

841
01:33:04,919 --> 01:33:08,409
...a woman's place is at her husband's feet.
一個女人的地位就是他丈夫的腳

842
01:33:16,869 --> 01:33:18,459
These two can be such children.
這兩個真是孩子

843
01:33:18,669 --> 01:33:21,999
They spend half their time fighting. The other half making up.
他們一半時間吵架, 一半時間和解

844
01:33:22,699 --> 01:33:25,399
Sweetie-pie, can't you stay a while longer?
甜餅, 你就不能久待會?

845
01:33:25,969 --> 01:33:29,339
No, I have to go...
不行, 我必須要走..

846
01:33:29,679 --> 01:33:31,109
SWEETIE -PIE!
甜餅!

847
01:33:35,119 --> 01:33:36,209
Shut up guys.
行了, 夥計們

848
01:33:41,319 --> 01:33:42,879
Shut up yaar... Ma will hear everything.
閉嘴啊, 媽都聽到了

849
01:33:45,529 --> 01:33:48,519
I know how Sonia must be feeling right now...
我知道Sue現在的感受

850
01:33:48,729 --> 01:33:50,219
...my father was also in the army.
我父親以前也在軍隊

851
01:33:50,699 --> 01:33:52,859
I used to think that way too...
我也曾經這樣想

852
01:33:53,769 --> 01:33:56,289
...when Ajay's father and I first got married.
當時我跟Ajay他爸新婚

853
01:33:57,039 --> 01:34:00,229
But then you realize something about being an Air-force pilot's wife.
然後想到做空軍飛行員的妻子

854
01:34:00,669 --> 01:34:05,509
You realize that your husband has pledged his life forthe country.
想到丈夫已經把生命交給了國家

855
01:34:06,909 --> 01:34:12,609
The least you can do for him, is control your emotions. Not be weak.
你能為他做的, 就是控制情緒不要脆弱

856
01:34:22,859 --> 01:34:26,189
I'm so happy Ajay's chosen a girl like you...
我很高興, Ajay選了你這樣的好女孩

857
01:34:26,399 --> 01:34:28,229
...now I can die in peace.
現在我可以安心死了

858
01:34:28,439 --> 01:34:29,059
Don't talk nonsense Ma.
說什麼呢, 媽

859
01:34:29,269 --> 01:34:33,669
You'll have many more years... ...and a dozen grandchildren too.
你還有很多時間, 跟很多孫子孫女呢

860
01:34:33,939 --> 01:34:36,569
Grandchildren? First you've got to stay home long enough to make them, dude.
孫子孫女? 要有足夠時間來造人啊

861
01:35:07,009 --> 01:35:11,999
The bugle sounds, the enemy wakes. The battle is upon us.
號角鳴響, 敵人出動, 戰鬥已來臨

862
01:35:14,419 --> 01:35:19,379
And in our hearts, we feel the swell, of pride and steel and valour.
我們心裏, 自豪堅定, 和英勇在膨脹

863
01:35:21,759 --> 01:35:26,689
For we will play the game of blood, if dark clouds shroud our land.
烏雲籠罩了大地, 我們誓死血戰

864
01:35:29,059 --> 01:35:34,399
Because this day, we walk with death, and laugh at its pale spectre.
因為今日與死亡同行, 嘲笑它蒼白臉龐

865
01:35:40,439 --> 01:35:44,969
We will not fear those cruel swords, our courage is far sharper.
我們不懼怕殘忍尖刀, 勇氣更為鋒利

866
01:35:46,579 --> 01:35:51,569
We will not lower, in the face of threats, a head raised to its mother.
面對威脅絕不屈服, 仰頭向祖國母親

867
01:35:55,119 --> 01:35:59,989
We will not fear those cruel swords, our courage is far sharper.
我們不懼怕殘忍尖刀, 勇氣更為鋒利

868
01:36:02,499 --> 01:36:07,019
We will not lower, in the face of threats, a head raised to its mother.
面對威脅絕不屈服, 仰頭向祖國母親

869
01:36:09,739 --> 01:36:14,969
For let them know, their cowardly deeds, just serve to stoke our fires.
讓他們知道怯懦行徑, 只會火上澆油

870
01:36:17,079 --> 01:36:22,209
Because this day, we walk with death, and laugh at its pale spectre.
因為今日與死亡同行, 嘲笑它蒼白臉龐

871
01:36:25,719 --> 01:36:30,279
We bade farewell, to this day, knowing it could be our last.
我們今天互相道別, 了知是自身的終結

872
01:36:30,759 --> 01:36:35,249
We swore to play, with our lives, never waver in our task.
我們發誓獻出生命, 在戰鬥中絕不退縮

873
01:36:35,559 --> 01:36:40,229
For we are but the last, few guests, served at fate's great banquet.
因在這命運的筵席, 我們是最後的賓客

874
01:36:40,499 --> 01:36:45,109
We cannot quell, the raging storm, the spirit of revolution.
無法鎮壓狂怒的風暴, 是這革命的精神

875
01:36:45,419 --> 01:36:50,139
For it now courses in our veins, like lava truly molten.
它流淌在我們的血液, 就像熔岩在滾動

876
01:36:50,509 --> 01:36:55,139
We will teach them, the twin lessons, of fear and fortitude.
我們給他們兩個教訓, 便是恐懼和堅毅

877
01:36:55,349 --> 01:36:59,809
Our goal cannot now hide for long, when courage is our beacon.
我們的目標埋藏不住, 勇敢是我們燈塔

878
01:37:00,019 --> 01:37:04,819
Because this day, we walk with death, and laugh at its pale spectre.
因為今日與死亡同行, 嘲笑它蒼白臉龐

879
01:37:08,889 --> 01:37:13,009
The entire country is in deep mourning of the Lalaji's death
整個國家都在悼念Lalaji的戰亡

880
01:37:13,629 --> 01:37:15,589
Just before his death, Lalaji had said
就在Lalaji死前, 他說

881
01:37:16,089 --> 01:37:21,159
Every blow ended me, is a nail in the coffin of British imperialism
每次抗擊都是英帝國主義棺材上的一顆釘

882
01:37:23,619 --> 01:37:25,389
It was the calm before the storm
是暴風雨來臨前的寧靜

883
01:37:29,519 --> 01:37:31,979
We have to take drastic measures.
我們必須採取嚴厲的措施

884
01:37:33,019 --> 01:37:33,819
What drastic measures?
什麼意思?

885
01:37:36,989 --> 01:37:38,009
Kill him.
幹掉他

886
01:38:01,179 --> 01:38:01,799
Com'on.
走

887
01:38:29,209 --> 01:38:32,509
Bhagat run! Quick!
Bhagat, 跑! 快!

888
01:38:33,729 --> 01:38:36,619
You! Get going.
你來啊, 如果想死的話

889
01:38:54,899 --> 01:38:55,979
On the day that followed
接下來的第二天

890
01:38:56,619 --> 01:38:58,869
Azad, Bhagat Singh and others went missing
Azad, Bhagat Singh和其他人都不見了

891
01:39:00,229 --> 01:39:02,149
This was the period when they coin the 2 words
正是這時他們創造了新詞

892
01:39:03,309 --> 01:39:04,749
Inquilab Zindabad
Inquilab Zindabad (革命萬歲)

893
01:39:07,729 --> 01:39:09,209
Inquilab Zindabad
Inquilab Zindabad

894
01:39:09,579 --> 01:39:13,569
Two words that became the slogan for the Indian freedom movement.
這個詞成了印度自由運動的口號

895
01:39:19,259 --> 01:39:21,019
Great idea!
好主意!

896
01:39:21,359 --> 01:39:23,419
But Bhagat, escaping will be impossible.
但Bhagat, 這樣沒法逃脫

897
01:39:23,629 --> 01:39:24,919
Our main mission is to get caught...
我們主要的任務是被抓..

898
01:39:25,459 --> 01:39:27,789
...not escape.
而不是逃脫

899
01:39:27,999 --> 01:39:28,559
What?
什麼?

900
01:39:29,629 --> 01:39:32,759
If we get caught there will be a trial...
如果被抓將會有審判

901
01:39:33,499 --> 01:39:35,169
...we'll get a chance to speak.
我們有機會發言

902
01:39:36,039 --> 01:39:37,029
We'll be heard.
將會被聽到

903
01:39:43,649 --> 01:39:47,379
But if they catch us, they'll hang us for certain.
可如果被抓, 一定會被絞死

904
01:39:47,789 --> 01:39:48,439
I know.
我知道

905
01:39:50,889 --> 01:39:54,329
But it takes a loud noise to open deaf ears.
要開啟聾子耳朵, 需要有力的呼喊

906
01:40:01,429 --> 01:40:03,239
LONG LIVE THE REVOLUTION!
Inquilab Zindabad (革命萬歲)!

907
01:40:03,239 --> 01:40:04,579
Smoke bombs
他們用了煙霧彈

908
01:40:05,339 --> 01:40:07,629
intended to awaken England from her dreams
想讓英格蘭從美夢中甦醒

909
01:40:08,989 --> 01:40:10,809
And they had more than achieve their task
而他們遠不止達成了目標

910
01:40:10,849 --> 01:40:11,839
DOWN WITH IMPERIALISM!
帝國主義滅亡!

911
01:40:22,619 --> 01:40:29,879
Feel the unrest
"感受這躁動.."

912
01:40:52,319 --> 01:40:54,549
The embers, they are burning.
"餘燼在燃燒"

913
01:40:54,749 --> 01:40:59,549
The tide, it's turning. You can feel the winds of change
"潮兒在漲動, 風兒在轉向"

914
01:40:59,759 --> 01:41:01,729
Feel the unrest sweep through the land Feel the unrest
"感受這躁動.."

915
01:41:12,839 --> 01:41:14,239
We are political prisoners...
我們是政治犯

916
01:41:15,869 --> 01:41:18,929
...we should be allowed books... ...writing material...
應該可以給我們書本, 紙筆

917
01:41:19,339 --> 01:41:22,339
...and at least one daily newspaper.
還有至少一份新聞日報

918
01:41:22,549 --> 01:41:25,809
We will not eat till then. The hunger strike will continue.
拿不到就禁食, 會繼續抗議

919
01:41:37,409 --> 01:41:40,899
The fast and torture went on for 114 days
禁食和拷打持續了114天

920
01:41:41,239 --> 01:41:43,239
114 days
114天!

921
01:41:44,229 --> 01:41:48,239
Never before in the history of any revolution that anyone last it so long
史上任何革命任何人也沒有持續過這麼久

922
01:41:49,269 --> 01:41:51,339
in such a human conditions
在這樣的狀態下

923
01:41:53,169 --> 01:41:54,739
We can crush these young boys
我們能摧毀他們的身體

924
01:41:55,999 --> 01:41:58,079
but we cannot crush their soul
但摧不毀他們的靈魂

925
01:41:58,579 --> 01:42:03,949
Our words won't falter now, We will speak our mind.
"言語不會畏懼, 我們道出心聲"

926
01:42:06,219 --> 01:42:11,419
We won't back down now. Our dreams we won't leave behind.
"夢想不會放棄, 我們不會退縮"

927
01:42:12,029 --> 01:42:20,199
We won't let the storm die. Injustice we will defy.
"風暴不會消亡, 我們反抗不公"

928
01:42:28,639 --> 01:42:37,809
You can feel it possess you now. Feel it, your soul, claim.
"感受它佔據你, 感受你的靈魂"

929
01:42:38,589 --> 01:42:42,819
Drink this spirit in one long swallow. Feel it course through your veins
"將這精神飲下, 感受它流淌全身"

930
01:42:43,429 --> 01:42:47,829
Let the celebrations begin now. Feel your body sway.
"讓這狂歡開始, 感受身體搖擺"

931
01:42:48,399 --> 01:42:52,839
In every breath feel more alive. To keep the storm at bay
"呼吸感受鮮活, 讓這風暴持續"

932
01:42:53,839 --> 01:42:58,499
See the unrest in those eyes. See it all around.
"眼裏看到這躁動, 掃過整個大地"

933
01:42:58,709 --> 01:43:03,169
See it in the air, my friend. And in those hearts, abound.
"還有心也在躁動, 感受這躁動"

934
01:43:03,649 --> 01:43:08,309
Feel the unrest sweep through the land
"眼裏看到這躁動, 掃過整個大地"

935
01:43:08,729 --> 01:43:12,999
See it in the air, my friend. And in those hearts, abound.
"還有心也在躁動, 感受這躁動"

936
01:43:23,629 --> 01:43:27,829
The winds of change are blowing now The tide it is, a turning.
"風兒它已經轉向, 潮水也在漲動"

937
01:43:28,039 --> 01:43:33,029
The moment of truth is upon us now It's time to do or die.
"為了真理而拚搏, 感受這躁動"

938
01:43:33,239 --> 01:43:42,669
We are engulfed in the shadows But we will come out brighter.
"我們被那陰影吞沒, 出來時會更明亮"

939
01:43:43,489 --> 01:43:52,759
Feel the unrest. Feel the unrest.
"感受這躁動.."

940
01:44:00,729 --> 01:44:01,319
Pretty huh?
漂亮吧?

941
01:44:03,789 --> 01:44:04,459
I like these ones
我喜歡它們

942
01:44:04,949 --> 01:44:05,969
I think I'll buy them
可能會買下來

943
01:44:09,849 --> 01:44:11,399
Pretty nice huh? Very pretty.
真的很漂亮

944
01:44:14,619 --> 01:44:17,209
In breaking news today...
現在報道最新新聞..

945
01:44:17,649 --> 01:44:21,949
...a MIG-21 fighter plane has just crashed...
一架MIG-21戰鬥機失事墜毀

946
01:44:22,259 --> 01:44:25,319
...this is the second such crash in the past six months...
這是六個月來發生的第二起事故

947
01:44:25,589 --> 01:44:29,119
The Defence Ministry has ordered an investigation into the crash.
國防部長已下令調查此事件

948
01:44:29,499 --> 01:44:32,519
We have just received news that the pilot...
我們剛剛收到消息, 飛行員..

949
01:44:32,769 --> 01:44:36,499
...Flight Lieutenant Ajay Rathod has died in the crash.
..Ajay Rathod上校在事故中遇難

950
01:44:38,069 --> 01:44:41,469
Flight Lt Rathod apparently did not eject from the burning plane...
Rathod上校沒有從飛機上跳傘..

951
01:44:41,679 --> 01:44:47,709
Instead he steered it away from Ambala city and crashed it in an open field.
而是將它開離Ambala, 墜毀在一片空地

952
01:44:47,919 --> 01:44:49,079
Thus saving many lives
以此挽救生命

953
01:44:50,089 --> 01:44:51,449
Viewers may recall...
觀眾也許還記得..

954
01:44:51,649 --> 01:44:55,749
...that until now, 163 MiG-21 of IAF have crashed...
到目前為止, 印度空軍已有163架MIG-21失事..

955
01:44:55,959 --> 01:44:59,919
...and 66 pilots have lost their lives.
66名飛行員喪生

956
01:46:15,569 --> 01:46:23,999
This game of hide and seek has gone on too long, come home now, won't you.
"這'捉迷藏'玩得太久, 現在回家來吧"

957
01:46:24,909 --> 01:46:28,869
I've searched high and low,
"我能去哪, 將你找尋"

958
01:46:29,449 --> 01:46:33,399
these old eyes are weary so, come home now won't you.
"你的母親已疲倦"

959
01:46:33,549 --> 01:46:37,949
Dusk is spreading like the ache in my heart,
"天色已晚, 我多麼擔心"

960
01:46:38,089 --> 01:46:45,469
my vision blurs, come home now won't you.
"淚眼矇矓, 快回家來吧"

961
01:46:48,639 --> 01:46:56,569
I'm in a place you wouldn't believe Ma.
"如何解釋我的所在, 媽"

962
01:46:57,849 --> 01:47:06,079
Endless skies I can soar.
"無盡的天空任我翱翔"

963
01:47:07,119 --> 01:47:15,759
Just like your fairy tales, it's filled with dreams.
"就像童話故事, 有著美麗, 純潔和夢幻"

964
01:47:15,759 --> 01:47:23,559
A sea of hope with no shore.
"我的風箏就在這裏, 無憂無慮飛翔"

965
01:47:24,939 --> 01:47:32,779
My soul flies here, like a kite without fear. No one to cut my strings, no more.
"希望沒人將線剪斷, 也不會被偷走"

966
01:47:33,149 --> 01:47:38,779
Flt. Lt. Ajay Rathod stayed in the plane until the very end...
Ajay Rathod上校始終堅持到最後

967
01:47:39,119 --> 01:47:43,279
...and steered the plane clear of Ambala city.
駕駛飛機飛離Ambala城

968
01:47:43,489 --> 01:47:48,539
Thereby saving many lives.
從而挽救了許多生命

969
01:47:48,739 --> 01:47:52,959
Unfortunately, the captain Ajay Rathod lost lives
然而Ajay Rathod上校卻犧牲了自己

970
01:47:52,969 --> 01:47:56,889
In the last 10 years over 100 MIG-21 aircrafts of the IAF have crashed...
過去12年印度空軍有100多架MIG-21飛機墜毀

971
01:47:56,889 --> 01:48:01,299
...in which over 30 pilots have lost their lives.
造成30多名飛行員喪生

972
01:48:01,329 --> 01:48:09,199
Defence Minister, CAG report says old & defective Russian spare parts were procured by the govt.
國防部長請告訴我們, CAG(審計總署)報告稱 政府使用的是俄國破舊的零部件

973
01:48:09,349 --> 01:48:12,149
Isn't this a case of high-level corruption?
這是否說明高層的腐敗?

974
01:48:12,159 --> 01:48:17,949
Not at all. I've personally clarified the issue in parliament.
不, 當然不是. 我親自向議會澄清過

975
01:48:18,419 --> 01:48:20,089
This is a downright lie.
這完全是污蔑

976
01:48:20,489 --> 01:48:23,429
The youngsters of today are brash and irresponsible when it comes to flying planes.
現在的年輕人飛行時輕率而不負責

977
01:48:23,629 --> 01:48:25,649
No! I don't agree...
不! 我不同意..

978
01:48:26,129 --> 01:48:28,599
Flt. Lt. Ajay Rathod was an ace pilot...
Ajay Rathod是個飛行能手..

979
01:48:28,799 --> 01:48:30,499
...who I trained...
是我調教的

980
01:48:30,899 --> 01:48:34,859
He was a gold medallist. The youngest to clear night sorties.
他獲得過金牌獎章, 是最年輕的夜間飛行員

981
01:48:35,069 --> 01:48:37,629
With over 1000 flying hours...
飛行超過1000小時

982
01:48:38,079 --> 01:48:40,939
This can't be the record of an irresponsible pilot.
沒有哪個不負責的飛行員能做到這點

983
01:48:41,209 --> 01:48:46,909
Defence Minister, how many more pilots will you send to their graves...
國防部長, 這體系的腐敗還會持續多久..

984
01:48:47,119 --> 01:48:54,819
...before you stop the rot in the system?
你還會葬送多少飛行員的性命..?

985
01:48:55,259 --> 01:49:04,289
If only I could show you this place, Ma.
"怎樣才能讓你看到這般景象"

986
01:49:04,569 --> 01:49:13,539
Here waterfalls are made of rainbows.
"我在這裏所喝的水, 來自瀑布"

987
01:49:13,749 --> 01:49:22,979
There are no roses just bouquets of dreams Ma. Their scent, no flower can hope for.
"我跳躍所觸及到的, 都是夢想"

988
01:49:23,189 --> 01:49:27,179
Here sunlight and shadow walk hand in hand.
"想找陰涼卻發覺並不炎熱"

989
01:49:27,659 --> 01:49:31,289
Everything seems bright and new.
"一切都是那樣地清新"

990
01:49:32,299 --> 01:49:36,699
But what is heaven, and all its wonders,
"在這什麼都有, 媽可是"

991
01:49:36,899 --> 01:49:42,099
when Ma, I don't have you.
"沒有你, 我覺得孤單"

992
01:49:42,309 --> 01:49:44,779
From now on, the government will make sure that...
從現在起, 政府會敕令..

993
01:49:45,679 --> 01:49:50,639
...only experienced pilots are given access to these machines...
只有經驗豐富的飛行員能駕駛這些飛機

994
01:49:51,249 --> 01:49:57,449
...and not to rash pilots like Ajay Rathod.
而不是像Ajay Rathod這樣魯莽的飛行員

995
01:49:57,719 --> 01:49:59,689
What the hell is he talking about!
他媽的在說些什麼!

996
01:49:59,889 --> 01:50:04,019
I welcome any investigation. I have nothing to hide.
我歡迎任何調查, 我沒什麼好隱藏

997
01:50:08,329 --> 01:50:12,499
This damn MIG investigation shouldn't take us down.
這該死的MiG調查不該影響我們

998
01:50:13,139 --> 01:50:18,799
Relax Sir. Public memory is short. Besides, we'll handle things.
放心先生, 公眾的記憶短暫, 何況還有我們呢

999
01:50:20,449 --> 01:50:25,039
Dead pilots, live very long in the news.
死去的飛行員, 媒體上會持續很久

1000
01:50:26,319 --> 01:50:29,249
But then, they join the forces to sacrifice their lives. Don't they?
然後人們就加入空軍去"犧牲", 不是嗎?

1001
01:51:38,019 --> 01:51:40,389
The situation is tense at the moment.
此刻形勢非常緊張

1002
01:51:40,659 --> 01:51:43,249
There is growing anger and discontent.
憤怒和不滿在增長

1003
01:51:43,459 --> 01:51:47,449
Directed largely towards the government. Especially the Defence Minister.
直接針對政府, 尤其是國防部長

1004
01:51:47,669 --> 01:51:49,629
We have with us Ajay Rathod's mother...
Ajay Rathod的母親就在這裏

1005
01:51:53,769 --> 01:51:55,969
The government can't wash its hands off the issue like this.
政府難逃其咎

1006
01:51:56,809 --> 01:51:59,169
They are answerable to the public.
他們應給公眾交待

1007
01:51:59,939 --> 01:52:05,469
If the MIG spare parts were of doubtful quality, why were they bought in the first place?
如果MiG的零件有質量隱患, 為什麼還要去買?

1008
01:52:05,849 --> 01:52:06,979
For what?
為了什麼?

1009
01:52:10,289 --> 01:52:11,809
Money?
為了錢嗎?

1010
01:52:13,079 --> 01:52:15,389
Money won't bring our children back.
但錢不能讓我兒子起死回生

1011
01:52:18,399 --> 01:52:22,769
The Defence Minister is morally responsible.
國防部長在道義上應受譴責

1012
01:52:23,569 --> 01:52:25,229
He has to resign.
他應該引退

1013
01:52:25,539 --> 01:52:29,169
It looks like the veil has been pulled off the defence scam.
看來國防部腐敗的面紗已被揭開

1014
01:52:29,369 --> 01:52:32,539
But how much will be revealed?
但是能暴露多少?

1015
01:52:32,739 --> 01:52:35,839
Mishra, what's happening?
Mishra, 是怎麼回事?

1016
01:52:52,999 --> 01:52:55,829
Ajay Rathod was not a novice...
Ajay Rathod不是個新手..

1017
01:52:56,029 --> 01:52:59,429
...he didn't let his plane crash into the town.
他沒有讓飛機墜落在城鎮

1018
01:53:00,139 --> 01:53:06,699
When it developed a snag he didn't try to save his life.
出現狀況時他沒有逃命

1019
01:53:07,509 --> 01:53:13,509
He steered it clear of Ambala ...saving thousands of civilians.
他駕離了Ambala, 救了上千的人民

1020
01:53:13,719 --> 01:53:20,519
Yet the Defence Minister calls him rash.
而國防部長卻稱他"輕率"

1021
01:53:39,209 --> 01:53:42,229
I'm not moving... this is for Ajay.
我不會走.. 這是為了Ajay

1022
01:53:43,849 --> 01:53:45,579
This could turn ugly, Aunty.
有可能變得不可收拾, 大嬸

1023
01:53:46,249 --> 01:53:47,049
Let it.
讓他們來吧

1024
01:54:11,669 --> 01:54:14,839
Our blood is ranging. It's flowing through the streets.
"為了改變這現狀"

1025
01:54:15,109 --> 01:54:17,979
But it won't go in vain
"血液在流淌"

1026
01:54:19,579 --> 01:54:26,509
