Someone get a doctor! Quick! We'll take it from here.
快去叫醫生, 這裏交給我們

1043
01:57:10,089 --> 01:57:12,439
Please patient, we'll take care
請在這耐心等候, 我們會處理

1044
01:57:33,509 --> 01:57:36,139
They were beating up innocent people...
他們在毆打群眾..

1045
01:57:37,909 --> 01:57:40,209
Why didn't you stop them?
你為什麼不阻止?

1046
01:57:40,579 --> 01:57:42,709
You protested against the government, our own party...
你抗議政府, 我們自己的黨

1047
01:57:42,919 --> 01:57:43,749
That's unacceptable.
是不可接受的

1048
01:57:44,649 --> 01:57:46,749
The protest was not against the government...
抗議不是針對政府..

1049
01:57:47,249 --> 01:57:48,949
...it was for the truth.
而是為了真相

1050
01:57:50,929 --> 01:57:52,949
So many pilots have died...
死了這麼多飛行員

1051
01:57:53,159 --> 01:57:56,189
...young innocent boys who were fighting for our country... killed...
他們為國家戰鬥犧牲

1052
01:57:56,429 --> 01:58:01,389
...so that someone in the government could make money.
而政府裏有人拿這個來賺錢

1053
01:58:02,099 --> 01:58:04,399
And our party office doesn't do a thing about it.
我們的黨卻無動於衷

1054
01:58:05,409 --> 01:58:06,129
Come... Sit down.
來, 坐

1055
01:58:11,609 --> 01:58:12,369
Have some tea.
喝茶

1056
01:58:19,119 --> 01:58:25,579
Laxman, in politics there's no place for emotions.
Laxman, 政治是沒有感情的

1057
01:58:26,459 --> 01:58:28,619
We have big plans for you.
我們對你有很高的期望

1058
01:58:29,759 --> 01:58:30,589
Big plans.
很高期望

1059
01:58:30,799 --> 01:58:36,169
Only dogs salivate when you show them bone Mishraji.
Mishraji, 扔塊骨頭, 只有哈巴狗才搖頭晃尾

1060
01:59:08,169 --> 01:59:09,189
How's Aunty?
大媽還好嗎?

1061
01:59:09,599 --> 01:59:10,729
They're doing an MRI.
他們在做MRI掃瞄

1062
01:59:30,189 --> 01:59:32,619
She's slipped into a coma.
她陷入了昏迷

1063
01:59:33,029 --> 01:59:38,289
Severe skull damage, coupled with the shock of her son's death.
嚴重的腦損傷, 加上兒子死去的打擊

1064
01:59:39,199 --> 01:59:43,689
That's an ugly gash. You need attention.
有一道很深的傷口, 要特別注意

1065
01:59:47,869 --> 01:59:50,069
Aslam... How's he?
Aslam, Aslam怎麼樣?

1066
01:59:54,709 --> 01:59:56,579
What have you come for? Haven't you done enough damage?
你們來幹什麼? 做得還不夠?

1067
02:00:01,219 --> 02:00:03,549
Uncle, it isn't what you think.
伯伯, 不是你想的那樣

1068
02:00:04,019 --> 02:00:08,959
I'm not interested in what you think, In what you want to do...
我不感興趣你想什麼, 要說什麼..

1069
02:00:10,899 --> 02:00:12,689
I'm just going to say this once.
我只說這一次

1070
02:00:13,369 --> 02:00:15,699
Aslam doesn't know what's good for him.
Aslam不知道什麼才對他好

1071
02:00:16,369 --> 02:00:18,769
He's an emotional boy, always has been. He listens to his heart, not his head.
他容易衝動, 做事隨心不動腦

1072
02:00:21,009 --> 02:00:23,439
These are bad times, for people like us.
像我們這樣的人不好過

1073
02:00:24,409 --> 02:00:28,209
Don't take him down with you.
不要連累了他

1074
02:00:30,149 --> 02:00:32,139
He's inside. Go on...
進來吧, 他在裏面

1075
02:00:52,269 --> 02:00:54,209
All parts working?
各個部分還能運轉吧?

1076
02:00:56,039 --> 02:00:59,009
Don't make me laugh, idiot. It hurts
別惹我笑, 傻瓜. 很痛

1077
02:01:00,209 --> 02:01:01,269
How's Aunty?
大媽怎麼樣?

1078
02:01:02,549 --> 02:01:03,569
She's in a coma.
在昏迷

1079
02:01:07,289 --> 02:01:09,009
How can this be happening to us?
這種事怎麼會發生在我們身上?

1080
02:01:22,029 --> 02:01:23,189
Some dinner?
吃點東西嗎?

1081
02:01:23,699 --> 02:01:25,899
No, don't worry Aunty.
不伯母, 不麻煩了

1082
02:01:26,869 --> 02:01:30,329
We just came to see Aslam. We've got to get back to the hospital.
我們剛從醫院出來, 就來看看Aslam

1083
02:01:31,079 --> 02:01:32,039
Take care.
保重

1084
02:01:56,769 --> 02:01:58,199
Listen... I...
聽著, 我..

1085
02:02:01,569 --> 02:02:02,619
...I'm sorry.
我想跟你說

1086
02:02:05,499 --> 02:02:06,139
sorry
對不起

1087
02:03:08,909 --> 02:03:09,959
Please eat.
吃吧

1088
02:03:33,229 --> 02:03:34,859
Everything's falling apart...
什麼都一團糟

1089
02:03:37,669 --> 02:03:39,529
...and all I can do is stand and watch.
我只能站著看

1090
02:03:46,779 --> 02:03:48,899
People like us don't count out here.
我們這樣的人不起作用

1091
02:03:53,399 --> 02:03:55,119
This system is so messed up
體系這麼糟糕

1092
02:03:56,699 --> 02:03:57,819
a hundred more Ajay's can die
死100多個"Ajay"也無濟於事

1093
02:04:00,249 --> 02:04:01,259
and nothing will change.
什麼也不會變

1094
02:04:31,939 --> 02:04:35,429
Ajay did everything right, all his life...
Ajay什麼都做得很對, 他的一生

1095
02:04:39,449 --> 02:04:46,509
...he was a good pilot, a good friend, a good son...
他是個好飛行員, 好朋友, 好兒子

1096
02:04:47,359 --> 02:04:49,649
...he never harmed a soul.
從沒傷害過任何生命

1097
02:04:51,229 --> 02:04:57,759
...he didn't deserve this...
他不該是這個下場

1098
02:04:59,569 --> 02:05:01,629
...Sonia didn't deserve this...
Sonia也不該承受這痛苦

1099
02:05:16,089 --> 02:05:17,939
As I watch DJ sleep that night
那晚當我看著DJ睡覺

1100
02:05:18,639 --> 02:05:20,059
A funny thought caught me
我冒出了個奇怪的想法

1101
02:05:21,829 --> 02:05:23,219
Maybe DJ wasn't sleeping
也許DJ沒有睡去

1102
02:05:24,379 --> 02:05:25,469
Maybe none of them were
也許他們沒人是

1103
02:05:26,949 --> 02:05:29,289
Maybe they were all waking up
也許他們都在覺醒

1104
02:06:09,469 --> 02:06:12,929
Hey Karan... they've spoilt your jacket.
Karan, 他們在糟蹋你的夾克

1105
02:06:14,109 --> 02:06:15,509
Long live India!
印度萬歲!

1106
02:06:48,039 --> 02:06:50,369
The scoundrel got away with it again.
那個混蛋又逃脫了

1107
02:06:51,079 --> 02:06:52,699
There's nothing can we do...
我們什麼都做不了

1108
02:06:54,149 --> 02:06:55,979
...when the law of the land protects people like the Defence Minister.
當法律偏向這樣的人..

1109
02:06:59,089 --> 02:07:01,649
We have to take drastic measures.
我們就得採取嚴厲的行動

1110
02:07:03,119 --> 02:07:04,279
What do you mean?
什麼意思?

1111
02:07:05,389 --> 02:07:06,789
Do what?
要怎麼做?

1112
02:07:10,429 --> 02:07:11,589
Kill him.
殺掉他

1113
02:07:14,029 --> 02:07:14,929
What?
什麼?

1114
02:07:15,869 --> 02:07:17,199
Kill the Defence Minister!
殺掉國防部長

1115
02:07:18,369 --> 02:07:19,159
Are you crazy?
你們都瘋了?

1116
02:07:20,509 --> 02:07:21,969
We aren't killers Sonia.
我們不是殺人犯, Sonia

1117
02:07:22,169 --> 02:07:23,539
But they are.
但他們是

1118
02:07:23,839 --> 02:07:25,279
Have you lost it Karan!
你也瘋了, Karan?

1119
02:07:25,479 --> 02:07:27,609
It's not a blood lust...
這不是殺戮的慾望..

1120
02:07:28,549 --> 02:07:29,779
...it's a matter of justice.
而是為了正義

1121
02:07:29,979 --> 02:07:31,449
I'll get the gun.
我去搞槍

1122
02:07:31,649 --> 02:07:36,519
Don't fuel things, Pandey. We can't start killing people for any small reason.
不要火上澆油Pandey, 我們不能為了點小事殺人

1123
02:07:37,319 --> 02:07:40,089
You think Ajay's death is a small reason?
你覺得Ajay的死是小事?

1124
02:07:40,559 --> 02:07:42,219
Ajay's mother is a small reason?
Ajay的媽是小事?

1125
02:07:42,529 --> 02:07:45,429
You've got to understand Karan.
你要理解一下, Karan

1126
02:07:45,869 --> 02:07:47,969
Lala Lajpat Rai's death has to be avenged.
必須要為Lala Lajpat Rai的死報仇

1127
02:07:48,169 --> 02:07:49,629
Scott has to be killed.
Scott必須死

1128
02:07:49,839 --> 02:07:50,769
But...
可是..

1129
02:08:00,309 --> 02:08:05,809
