我們都瘋了?

1133
02:08:21,599 --> 02:08:23,519
He takes a morning walk at 8 a.m. Everyday
他每天早上8點要散步

1134
02:08:25,129 --> 02:08:26,059
We'll kill him then.
我們在那時動手

1135
02:08:26,509 --> 02:08:32,409
Who's we, huh? Who's going to pull the trigger?
到時動手! 誰來動手? 我們誰來動手?

1136
02:08:32,839 --> 02:08:33,739
I'll do it!
我

1137
02:08:37,149 --> 02:08:41,409
Even though the morning security is relaxed there is still a danger of getting caught.
雖然早上警衛鬆懈, 但還是有被抓的危險

1138
02:08:41,689 --> 02:08:45,019
There is no looking back now!
現在沒機會回頭了

1139
02:09:29,099 --> 02:09:38,069
The Defence Minister was on his morning walk when two unidentified gunmen opened fire.
今天早上國防部長在散步時 兩個身份不明的持槍人向他開槍

1140
02:09:38,339 --> 02:09:43,979
He was hit by three bullets in his chest, and was declared dead as he reached the hospital.
他胸口中了三槍, 在去醫院途中死亡

1141
02:09:44,179 --> 02:09:46,239
No group has yet claimed responsibility for this incident.
沒有組織聲明對此負責

1142
02:09:54,959 --> 02:09:59,919
Government spokespersons believe that this is an attempt to destablise the government.
政府發言人認為這是試圖影響政府穩定

1143
02:10:01,699 --> 02:10:07,069
The country has lost a great leader because of the cowardly act of some terrorists.
因為某些膽小的恐怖行徑, 國家失去了一位偉大領袖

1144
02:10:07,639 --> 02:10:09,659
He was a true soldier, a true patriot.
他是個真正的愛國將士

1145
02:10:09,869 --> 02:10:17,839
His contribution to the country cannot be described in words.
他對國家的貢獻無法用言語表達

1146
02:10:19,149 --> 02:10:20,169
Sukhi!
Sukhi!

1147
02:10:22,219 --> 02:10:24,519
Meanwhile our sources have discovered a telephonic conversation...
同時我們的線報捕獲了一次電話通話

1148
02:10:24,719 --> 02:10:28,349
...involving middle man Rajnath Singhania in an arms deal.
證明了中間商Rajnath Singhania參與了軍火交易

1149
02:10:28,659 --> 02:10:33,289
This conversation took place just a few days before the Defence Minister's assassination.
通話就發生在國防部長被刺的幾天前

1150
02:10:33,499 --> 02:10:37,189
The Russians want us to reduce our commission.
'俄國人想降低我們的佣金'

1151
02:10:37,499 --> 02:10:41,629
Didn't you tell them, its not a defence deal, but our deal.
'你沒跟他們說, 這不是國防部的交易, 而是我們的交易'

1152
02:10:42,239 --> 02:10:45,369
That's why I told them. - "Take it or leave it"
'所以我跟他們說, 他們自己看著辦'

1153
02:10:45,579 --> 02:10:49,099
Let's go.
我們走

1154
02:11:05,999 --> 02:11:07,219
Paaji, where's DJ?
Paaji, DJ在哪?

1155
02:11:07,429 --> 02:11:09,369
They were just here.
他們剛才還在這

1156
02:11:14,669 --> 02:11:16,609
He hasn't come home all night.
他整晚都沒回來

1157
02:11:20,179 --> 02:11:21,699
Is everything alright?
沒什麼事吧?

1158
02:11:23,879 --> 02:11:27,479
He said he'd be spending the night at DJ's.
他說要在DJ那過夜

1159
02:11:40,999 --> 02:11:42,429
Have you seen DJ?
看見DJ嗎?

1160
02:11:45,799 --> 02:11:48,099
Is everything alright?
沒事吧?

1161
02:11:48,279 --> 02:11:49,169
I can't find him
我找不到他

1162
02:11:49,439 --> 02:11:52,599
I can't find anyone, Sonia, or Aslam I don't know where they are
我誰都找不到, Sonia, Aslam, 不知道他們在哪

1163
02:11:53,299 --> 02:11:55,469
Come with me...
過來..

1164
02:11:57,909 --> 02:11:58,579
Sit
坐

1165
02:12:01,879 --> 02:12:05,179
Don't worry... nothing will happen to those boys...
別擔心.. 他們會沒事的

1166
02:12:06,489 --> 02:12:08,959
Daljeet has always been a brat...
Daljeet就是這麼淘氣

1167
02:12:09,159 --> 02:12:14,359
...he used to disappear on his bike for days...
他曾經開著摩托車, 消失好幾天

1168
02:12:20,839 --> 02:12:22,309
I'm scared...
我害怕..

1169
02:12:22,869 --> 02:12:25,469
Don't be afraid...
不要怕

1170
02:12:25,839 --> 02:12:28,039
God will take care of everything...
老天會保佑他們的

1171
02:12:29,679 --> 02:12:35,479
God watches over the people we love.
我們愛的人, 老天會照顧他們

1172
02:12:46,529 --> 02:12:48,159
Defence Minister... the martyr...
國防部長, 烈士..

1173
02:12:52,029 --> 02:12:56,969
...one of India's favourite sons... Scoundrel!
印度最可愛的兒子..

1174
02:12:58,369 --> 02:13:01,339
They're honouring him with the National Medal of Honour.
他們要給他國家榮譽勳章

1175
02:13:01,879 --> 02:13:05,909
All our efforts, wasted.
我們的努力, 白費了

1176
02:13:06,719 --> 02:13:08,549
People need to know the truth.
人們需要知道真相

1177
02:13:08,749 --> 02:13:11,019
...and who's going to tell them the truth?
是嗎? 誰去說出真相?

1178
02:13:11,219 --> 02:13:13,949
We have to surrender ourselves.
我們! 我們要去自首

1179
02:13:14,219 --> 02:13:14,949
What?
什麼?

1180
02:13:17,639 --> 02:13:25,229
Terriffic! You want us to walk right in and give ourselves up!
警官, 抓我吧, 抓我吧, 我們要自首

1181
02:13:25,429 --> 02:13:26,629
And who should we surrenderto?
我們跟誰自首?

1182
02:13:26,839 --> 02:13:29,359
The police are mere puppets.
警察, 不過是受制於人

1183
02:13:29,569 --> 02:13:32,629
Should we just sit back?
那怎麼辦? 就這樣坐著? 什麼也不做?

1184
02:13:32,839 --> 02:13:36,469
No! Let's kill them all!
不! 把他們都殺了!

1185
02:13:36,679 --> 02:13:38,009
Right Pandey?
是嗎 Pandey?

1186
02:13:38,209 --> 02:13:39,879
Someone make him shut up!
誰讓他閉嘴!

1187
02:13:48,789 --> 02:13:50,879
You always knew that your father was in it.
你早就知道你爸有份

1188
02:13:52,599 --> 02:13:53,889
You knew everything.
你什麼都知道

1189
02:13:57,099 --> 02:13:57,899
No Sukhi...
我不知道, Sukhi..

1190
02:13:58,099 --> 02:14:01,469
You're lying!
你在說謊!

1191
02:14:02,169 --> 02:14:04,159
You always wanted to take revenge on your father.
你一直想向你爸報仇

1192
02:14:04,369 --> 02:14:05,269
Sukhi, shut up!
Sukhi, 不要說了!

1193
02:14:05,469 --> 02:14:10,039
Who am I to say anything?
我是誰, 憑什麼說他?

1194
02:14:10,779 --> 02:14:14,739
DJ he's used you...
DJ他是在利用你

1195
02:14:15,449 --> 02:14:20,509
...he's used all of us...
利用了我們所有人

1196
02:14:21,019 --> 02:14:25,429
Mark my words, his father will bail him out.
記住我說的話, 他爸會保他出去

1197
02:14:25,629 --> 02:14:28,149
But we'll get caught. And I don't want to die DJ...
我們會被抓, 而我還不想死..

1198
02:14:28,359 --> 02:14:30,799
I don't want to die.
我不想死..

1199
02:14:37,809 --> 02:14:39,799
We did all this for Ajay.
我們這麼做都是為了Ajay

1200
02:14:44,179 --> 02:14:45,539
What will happen now DJ?
現在怎麼辦DJ?

1201
02:14:54,189 --> 02:14:55,589
You've decided?
你想好了?

1202
02:14:58,489 --> 02:14:59,649
I need to know the truth...
我得知道真相..

1203
02:15:01,599 --> 02:15:02,089
don't worry.
別擔心

1204
02:15:03,499 --> 02:15:06,929
I'm not worried. Just don't be late.
我不擔心, 只是別太晚

1205
02:15:22,579 --> 02:15:24,019
Nothing will happen to you Karan.
你不會有事的Karan

1206
02:15:24,789 --> 02:15:26,129
That's a promise.
我向你保證不會有事的

1207
02:15:27,289 --> 02:15:29,809
Just give me the names of the others.
只要把其它人的名字告訴我

1208
02:15:31,029 --> 02:15:36,929
I'll get you the best lawyers, pull all the strings possible.
我會請最好的律師, 想盡一切辦法

1209
02:15:37,769 --> 02:15:43,099
You were forced into it, do you understand? You were forced.
你是被逼的, 知道嗎? 是被逼的

1210
02:15:43,369 --> 02:15:44,569
And then you are out of this country
然後你就離開這個國家

1211
02:15:47,609 --> 02:15:50,309
Do you get me?
說話啊? 聽到沒有?

1212
02:15:51,329 --> 02:15:52,629
Say something, damn it
說話啊, 媽的!

1213
02:15:52,849 --> 02:15:56,149
Your father's reputation, his life's work is at stake.
你父親的名譽, 一生的事業都危在旦夕

1214
02:15:56,579 --> 02:15:58,639
Why did you do it?
你為什麼這麼做? 為什麼?

1215
02:16:02,159 --> 02:16:03,149
Why did you do it, Dad?
你為什麼這麼做?

1216
02:16:03,359 --> 02:16:06,119
What did I do?
我? 我做什麼了?

1217
02:16:06,959 --> 02:16:11,519
Ajay always said, "I'll give my life for this country."
Ajay總是說, "我會為國家獻身"

1218
02:16:12,499 --> 02:16:17,029
"...I'm not afraid of death."
"我不害怕死亡, 什麼也不怕"

1219
02:16:23,459 --> 02:16:27,239
and all you can think of is sending me out of the country...
而你想的, 卻是逃亡出國

1220
02:16:29,099 --> 02:16:33,839
Ajay was burnt alive...
Ajay他被活活燒死

1221
02:16:34,959 --> 02:16:36,649
You killed him!
是你殺了他

1222
02:16:37,589 --> 02:16:39,959
You made a joke of his death...
你把他的生命當兒戲

1223
02:16:40,189 --> 02:16:42,789
I know you're very disturbed...
我知道你很難受

1224
02:16:43,259 --> 02:16:46,829
Relax! Let me handle things.
但你什麼也不要想, 這事我來處理

1225
02:16:49,599 --> 02:16:52,299
I'll find a way out.
我會想到辦法的

1226
02:16:53,209 --> 02:16:54,469
Really Dad? Is there a way out?
只有一個辦法, 爸

1227
02:16:54,709 --> 02:16:57,039
Of course.
當然

1228
02:17:01,739 --> 02:17:03,339
You are going out of this country tonight
你今晚就出國

1229
02:18:05,849 --> 02:18:09,369
You don't have to do this...
Sukhi, 你沒必要這麼做

1230
02:18:13,719 --> 02:18:16,649
Sukhi, this might end badly.
Sukhi, 結局可能很糟糕

1231
02:18:19,089 --> 02:18:24,189
Without you guys it will end for me anyway...
反正沒有你們, 我也一樣糟糕

1232
02:18:25,359 --> 02:18:26,459
Idiot.
傻小子

1233
02:18:37,809 --> 02:18:44,679
Ajay's death, won't go in vain, Ma. I promise you.
媽, 我答應你, Ajay不會白死的

1234
02:18:47,429 --> 02:18:50,069
What is it about these boys that makes them have no fear?
是什麼讓這些人毫無畏懼?

1235
02:18:55,259 --> 02:18:57,799
I think sometimes a person can be pushed so far
我想有時一個人能走這麼遠

1236
02:18:58,239 --> 02:18:59,989
that will to place beyond the fear
到達超越恐懼的地步

1237
02:19:00,849 --> 02:19:03,409
A place where find strange peace
在那裏找到奇怪的安寧

1238
02:19:04,459 --> 02:19:06,719
where you'll free yourself to do the right thing
可以自由地做正確的事

1239
02:19:08,719 --> 02:19:09,569
Because sometimes, that's the hardest thing to do
因為有時, 這也是最難做到的事

1240
02:19:15,379 --> 02:19:16,139
Then I prayed for it
然後我祈禱

1241
02:19:16,969 --> 02:19:18,009
I prayed for forgiveness
祈求原諒

1242
02:19:20,789 --> 02:19:26,459
This is Rahul, and you've tuned in to your favourite radio show...
歡迎回來, 這裏是... 你最喜歡的電台, 我是Rahul..

1243
02:20:49,069 --> 02:20:52,399
Hey Karan! What're you doing here?
Karan, 真叫人驚喜! 你們怎麼來了?

1244
02:20:52,839 --> 02:20:53,969
We need a favour.
我們要你幫個忙

1245
02:20:54,179 --> 02:20:55,199
Sure!
當然

1246
02:20:55,549 --> 02:20:56,809
I need you to put us on air.
我們需要上電台

1247
02:20:58,019 --> 02:21:01,819
Put you on air?
上廣播電台?

1248
02:21:02,019 --> 02:21:03,819
Yeah, now!
是, 直播!

1249
02:21:04,259 --> 02:21:07,819
That's impossible man... I'll lose my job.
'是, 現在, 直播'那是不可能的, 我會丟工作的

1250
02:21:08,029 --> 02:21:09,649
...as it is, they don't pay me.
而且其實他們不付我錢

1251
02:21:11,029 --> 02:21:13,329
It's payback time.
那麼現在該付你了

1252
02:21:13,529 --> 02:21:17,659
Hey! Whateveryou say DJ! It's your station.
好吧好吧, 你怎麼說都好DJ! 電台都是你的

1253
02:21:19,539 --> 02:21:21,229
Gun... He's got a gun!
槍! 他有槍!

1254
02:21:21,439 --> 02:21:23,669
Karan you go in. I'll handle it.
Karan你進去, 我來處理

1255
02:21:25,039 --> 02:21:30,449
Keep the show on. Don't mess with us.
繼續播音, 別耍花招, 知道嗎?

1256
02:21:34,049 --> 02:21:36,519
Come on... leave.
來, 走吧

1257
02:21:39,589 --> 02:21:41,019
Paaji is anyone inside?
Paaji, 裏面還有人嗎?

1258
02:21:43,389 --> 02:21:46,689
Uncleji run. Don't stop.
Uncleji, 走, 別停下

1259
02:21:48,399 --> 02:21:52,199
Gun... Security he's got a gun!
槍.. 保安他有槍!

1260
02:21:53,969 --> 02:21:55,869
Don't be a wise guy.
別自作聰明

1261
02:21:56,069 --> 02:22:02,479
Everybody leave! Out! Move!
每個人都出去!

1262
02:22:02,679 --> 02:22:05,379
Don't panic we won't harm anyone.
別慌張, 我們不會傷害任何人

1263
02:22:05,579 --> 02:22:13,489
Move! Move! Move!
走走!

1264
02:22:14,829 --> 02:22:18,289
Hurry up, quick!
快點, 快!

1265
02:22:36,949 --> 02:22:43,479
The time is 6:05 a.m. And you're listening to "The night is still young".
現在是早上6點05分. 你現正收聽的是"夜色仍淡"

1266
02:22:43,689 --> 02:22:46,589
Today I've got a surprise guest for you.
今天我們請到了一個特殊嘉賓

1267
02:22:46,959 --> 02:22:51,419
An old friend of mine Karan Singhania, who just dropped in to say something to all of you...
我的一個老朋友Karan Singhania, 有話與大家分享

1268
02:22:59,169 --> 02:23:05,339
My name is Karan Singhania... My friends and I... we killed the Defence Minister...
我叫Karan Singhania, 我和我的朋友殺死了國防部長

1269
02:23:07,039 --> 02:23:11,309
I repeat we killed the Defence Minister...
我再說一遍, 我和我的朋友殺死了國防部長

1270
02:23:11,509 --> 02:23:14,849
Ravi take me to the radio station quickly. Hurry up!
Ravi馬上帶我去廣播站, 趕快!

1271
02:23:15,249 --> 02:23:20,309
We are not terrorists. We aren't backed by any foreign organisation.
我們不是恐怖分子, 背後也沒有什麼國外組織

1272
02:23:21,329 --> 02:23:23,229
We don't even belong to any political group...
我們不屬於任何下政治組織

1273
02:23:24,929 --> 02:23:26,949
We're just five students from Delhi University.
我們只是德裏大學的5個學生

1274
02:23:27,999 --> 02:23:30,299
We killed the Defense Minister because...
我們殺害了國防部長..

1275
02:23:31,569 --> 02:23:39,669
...he murdered ourfriend Flight Lieutenant Ajay Rathod and many other Air Force pilots...
因為他害死了我們的朋友Ajay Rathod上校 和其它很多的空軍飛行員

1276
02:23:40,009 --> 02:23:44,639
We killed him because after he murdered Ajay, he murdered his name...
我們殺了他因為他不僅害死了Ajay 還詆毀了他的名譽

1277
02:23:46,149 --> 02:23:56,989
Ajay's mother, right now, is fighting for her life...
Ajay的母親現在還在死亡線上掙扎

1278
02:23:59,929 --> 02:24:04,329
A Defence Minister is supposed to safegaurd a nation. Not sell it.
國防部長應該保衛國家, 而不是出賣國家

1279
02:24:05,699 --> 02:24:12,199
Men like the Defence Minister aren't just above the law... they control it.
像他那樣的人不僅凌駕法律之上, 而且一手操控

1280
02:24:13,209 --> 02:24:21,579
We killed him because someone had to say, "Enough!".
我們殺了他因為必須有人站出來抗議

1281
02:24:22,179 --> 02:24:23,669
We might be wrong...
我們也許錯了

1282
02:24:24,719 --> 02:24:26,749
...because its a sin to kill someone.
因為殺人是罪過

1283
02:24:27,859 --> 02:24:29,719
But we couldn't tolerate it anymore.
但我們再也忍受不了了

1284
02:24:30,629 --> 02:24:32,859
Today we are here to confess to our sin.
今天我們在此坦白我們的罪過

1285
02:24:34,199 --> 02:24:37,689
Today we are here to tell everybody that something has to be done
今天我們在此告訴每個人, 應該行動了

1286
02:24:39,669 --> 02:24:41,399
It's got to be done.
必須行動了

1287
02:24:44,669 --> 02:24:48,869
We've just received news that Defence Minister's assassins are hiding in All India Radio building.
我們剛得到消息國防部長的行刺者躲在"All India"廣播大樓

1288
02:24:49,309 --> 02:24:58,739
Karan Singhania and his friends are still with us. Listeners can call in on 3291777.
Karan Singhania與他的朋友仍然在線 聽眾可以撥打3291777

1289
02:24:59,459 --> 02:25:00,839
Until then, here is "Roobaroo"
先來段音樂

1290
02:25:10,029 --> 02:25:10,959
It's done.
說完了

1291
02:25:21,179 --> 02:25:22,799
Hey, dude!
"嘿夥計"

1292
02:25:25,009 --> 02:25:31,209
I just realized.
"現在明白了"

1293
02:25:33,189 --> 02:25:39,249
There's a fire burning within me.
"有一團火, 在胸中燃燒"

1294
02:25:41,099 --> 02:25:42,619
It's a new dawn,
"新的黎明"

1295
02:25:44,869 --> 02:25:47,429
I can feel its light
"感受到光線"

1296
02:25:49,109 --> 02:25:55,009
Burn so bright, I could, scorch the sun
"這麼明亮, 能把太陽烘烤"

1297
02:25:55,609 --> 02:26:11,189
'Cause I'm face to face with the light
"我與這光, 面對面"

1298
02:26:12,289 --> 02:26:18,349
The dream I once lost, I've found.
"這些夢想, 曾經失去"

1299
02:26:20,099 --> 02:26:26,469
It's blooming,
"重新找回, 它在盛放"

1300
02:26:28,209 --> 02:26:34,269
it's melting,
"猶如鋼鐵, 已經融化"

1301
02:26:36,149 --> 02:26:43,889
notes re-arranging,
"再次鍛造, 得到昇華"

1302
02:26:44,089 --> 02:26:51,559
into a whole new melody.
"它變成了, 星星的模樣"

1303
02:26:53,499 --> 02:26:55,199
Will they give us good food in jail?
監獄有好吃的嗎?

1304
02:26:57,609 --> 02:27:02,059
Food? Next he'll want beer.
好吃的? 接下來就想要啤酒了

1305
02:27:08,689 --> 02:27:12,779
You guys have become famous. Calls are pouring in from all overthe country.
你們出名了, 全國各地的電話都打來了

1306
02:27:12,989 --> 02:27:14,679
Come on! They want to talk to you...
來啊, 他們想跟你說話

1307
02:27:21,299 --> 02:27:21,919
Police!
警察!

1308
02:27:23,129 --> 02:27:25,759
This is unreal man. Where did they come from?
這不是真的. 他們從哪來的?

1309
02:27:25,969 --> 02:27:27,659
This will ruin my career...
我的事業要毀了

1310
02:27:27,869 --> 02:27:29,669
Shut up!
閉嘴

1311
02:27:31,009 --> 02:27:36,309
Karan you get on air... We don't have much time...
Karan你去播音.. 我們沒多少時間了

1312
02:27:36,509 --> 02:27:37,239
Take care.
保重

1313
02:27:42,749 --> 02:27:47,189
The Delhi police have reached the spot and are rescuing civilians trapped in the building.
德裏警方到達現場, 正對大樓被困的人進行救援

1314
02:27:54,129 --> 02:27:56,119
...reporting from Mumbai's Churchgate area...
..從孟買教堂門地區報道..

1315
02:27:56,329 --> 02:27:58,159
...reporting from Cotton College, Guwahati.
..從古瓦哈蒂的科頓大學報道..

1316
02:27:58,369 --> 02:28:00,229
...reporting from S. P. College, Srinagar...
..從斯利那加的S.P.大學報道..

1317
02:28:00,439 --> 02:28:04,229
...reporting from Lucknow University...
..從勒克瑙大學報道..

1318
02:28:04,939 --> 02:28:07,909
Hi, my name is Prakash. And I want to congratulate you.
我叫Prakash, 我想向你道賀

1319
02:28:08,109 --> 02:28:13,139
You did the right thing by killing him. All our ministers should be lined up and shot.
你們殺了他做得對, 所有部長都該排起隊來受死

1320
02:28:13,779 --> 02:28:17,219
Prakash, who all will you shoot?
Prakash, 你會殺掉哪一些部長?

1321
02:28:17,619 --> 02:28:22,489
These corrupt ministers are a reflection of our society. We've chosen them.
這些腐敗的部長是根據社會反映而選擇的

1322
02:28:25,929 --> 02:28:27,789
We need to change ourselves to bring about a change.
我們要改變自己從而帶來改變

1323
02:28:28,759 --> 02:28:33,219
Hello! This is Principal Sharma from Indore...
我是Indore的Sharma校長..

1324
02:28:33,569 --> 02:28:37,469
You have set a terrible example by taking the law into your own hands.
你們當自己是法律樹立了很壞的榜樣

1325
02:28:38,939 --> 02:28:42,429
You're right sir. We're sorry.
說得對, 我們很抱歉

1326
02:28:43,309 --> 02:28:48,909
But give me the name of one politician who has gone to jail for his crimes.
但是你說說有哪個政治家因為罪行入了監獄

1327
02:28:50,079 --> 02:28:51,709
Who else is on your hit-list? I
你的暗殺名單上還有誰?

1328
02:28:52,449 --> 02:28:53,889
We have no hit-list.
我們沒有暗殺名單

1329
02:28:55,259 --> 02:28:57,449
How do you feel after killing the Defence Minister?
殺掉了國防部長你有什麼感覺?

1330
02:28:57,659 --> 02:29:02,689
We did not kill him out of any blood lust...
我們殺了他不是出於殺戮欲

1331
02:29:21,519 --> 02:29:24,969
If you get caught you'll be hanged. Aren't you afraid?
如果被抓你們會被絞死, 你們不怕?

1332
02:29:25,949 --> 02:29:26,849
No.
不怕

1333
02:29:34,699 --> 02:29:38,389
The college students who have claimed responsibility...
聲稱對此負責的大學生

1334
02:29:38,599 --> 02:29:39,929
...are still inside.
還在裏面

1335
02:29:40,729 --> 02:29:47,999
Karan, while we applaud your courage, do you think you'll escape?
Karan, 當我們為你們的勇氣鼓掌時, 你們想過逃跑沒?

1336
02:29:48,509 --> 02:29:49,899
If we wanted to escape, we wouldn't have been here in the first place.
要是想逃就不來這了

1337
02:29:51,999 --> 02:29:53,019
Do not spare anyone.
一個也不要放過

1338
02:29:53,939 --> 02:29:55,459
I don't want any survivor
我不想有任何倖存者

1339
02:30:32,079 --> 02:30:35,449
Shit! They're shooting at us DJ! They're shooting at us!
我的老天, 他們在向我們開槍, DJ! ..

1340
02:30:35,659 --> 02:30:39,919
Shut up for a second!
冷靜一下!

1341
02:30:41,829 --> 02:30:44,959
They're mistaking us for terrorists. They think we're armed.
他們誤以為我們是恐怖分子, 以為我們有武器

1342
02:30:47,169 --> 02:30:51,999
Wait a minute! I'll try to handle it.
等一會, 我來處理

1343
02:31:16,069 --> 02:31:18,719
No Sukhi! What did you do!
看看你都做了什麼

1344
02:31:21,429 --> 02:31:25,599
Shit DJ! Just when I was getting good with the girls...
傻DJ, 我剛要和女孩子好上..

1345
02:31:48,859 --> 02:31:52,389
My name is Indra. What's the difference between you and a terrorist?
我叫Indra, 你們和恐怖分子有什麼區別呢?

1346
02:31:52,599 --> 02:31:58,729
There's a big difference. Terrorists kill innocent people. We didn't...
有很大區別, 恐怖分子殺害無辜的人, 我們沒有..

1347
02:32:12,149 --> 02:32:13,119
Aslam, close the door. Quick!
快關上門

1348
02:32:15,419 --> 02:32:17,319
We are not terrorists. Why don't they...
我們不是恐怖分子, 他們怎麼..

1349
02:33:09,139 --> 02:33:12,199
It's not a lust for blood... it's a matter of justice!
這不是殺戮欲, 而是為了正義

1350
02:33:12,709 --> 02:33:18,209
Why are bullets being used when its clear that these are college students?
已經很清楚是群大學生, 為什麼還要使用子彈?

1351
02:35:03,049 --> 02:35:11,979
No matter what you do, this country will never change. It has no future.
不管你們怎麼做, 國家都不會變化 這裏是印度, 它沒有未來

1352
02:35:15,359 --> 02:35:20,859
No country is perfect. You've got to make it perfect.
沒有國家是完美的, 只能讓它變得更好

1353
02:35:24,539 --> 02:35:30,599
Join the police, military, IAS...
加入警局, 軍隊, IAS(印度科學院)

1354
02:35:32,009 --> 02:35:34,779
Become a part of the political system...
成為政治體系的一分子

1355
02:35:37,389 --> 02:35:42,549
This country will change... We will change it!
國家會變的, 我們會改變她的

1356
02:35:44,459 --> 02:35:47,899
If you believed the Defence Minister deserved to be punished then...
如果你們相信國防部長應該受到懲罰..

1357
02:35:48,599 --> 02:35:52,629
...what about the allegations against your father? Why such double standards?
那你的父親呢? 怎麼說一套做一套?

1358
02:35:55,469 --> 02:35:56,799
We'll find a way to fix this.
我們會想出辦法來的

1359
02:35:58,469 --> 02:35:59,809
There's just one way to fix this Dad.
只有一個辦法, 爸

1360
02:36:19,629 --> 02:36:20,599
I'm sorry Dad...
對不起, 爸爸

1361
02:36:50,559 --> 02:36:52,029
My name is Daljeet Singh.
我叫Daljeet Singh.

1362
02:36:53,959 --> 02:36:56,019
There are only two ways to live your life.
生命有兩種活法

1363
02:36:57,229 --> 02:37:03,139
Tolerate things the way they are...
忍受現有的方式

1364
02:37:04,739 --> 02:37:08,699
...Ortake responsibility to change them.
或者, 負起責任來改變

1365
02:37:11,749 --> 02:37:17,379
Karan Singhania killed his father before coming here.
Karan Singhania來這之前已經殺了自己的父親

1366
02:37:29,239 --> 02:37:30,659
Shit DJ! You're bleeding badly!
你流了很多血!

1367
02:37:31,829 --> 02:37:38,029
Relax! It got tired of flowing in my veins. It just wanted to be free.
放鬆, 它在我血管裏待膩了, 它也想要自由

1368
02:37:40,039 --> 02:37:42,509
Aslam.. Laxman.. Sukhi?
Aslam... Laxman... Sukhi?

1369
02:37:43,779 --> 02:37:44,679
All gone.
都死了

1370
02:37:57,459 --> 02:38:01,759
...Karan, I think I'm in love...
Karan, 我想我戀愛了

1371
02:38:04,569 --> 02:38:06,119
...I nevertold you dude...
我從沒告訴過你們

1372
02:38:08,039 --> 02:38:11,299
...I can't stop thinking about her...
我止不住對她的思念

1373
02:38:15,179 --> 02:38:16,729
I know... she's something else.
我知道, 她與眾不同

1374
02:38:19,909 --> 02:38:22,469
You two'll make a great couple.
你們兩個會成為很配的一對

1375
02:38:27,889 --> 02:38:29,769
There's just one problem though.
只有一個問題

1376
02:38:31,879 --> 02:38:33,829
I don't know Whether the kids will be black or white.
我不知道孩子會是黑還是白

1377
02:38:58,849 --> 02:39:01,819
Let me go! They're just boys, damn it!
放開我! 他們不過是少年!

1378
02:39:13,709 --> 02:39:16,399
I always believe there were two kinds of men in this world
我一直認為世界上有兩種人

1379
02:39:18,379 --> 02:39:20,329
One who go to that death screaming
面對死亡哭喊的人

1380
02:39:21,799 --> 02:39:23,839
And men who go to that death in silence
面對死亡安靜的人

1381
02:39:27,409 --> 02:39:28,809
And then I met the third kind
然後我遇到了第三種

1382
02:40:16,529 --> 02:40:18,669
Sending commandos is the death of democracy
派出突擊隊是民主制度的死亡

1383
02:40:18,719 --> 02:40:21,529
Today is a sad day in the history of Indian politics
今天是印度政治歷史上悲傷的一天

1384
02:40:21,569 --> 02:40:24,229
We'll turn this spark into a raging fire.
我們會把這火花演變成熊熊火焰

1385
02:40:24,439 --> 02:40:27,639
This will swell like a wave and will bring an end to corruption.
這會像洶涌的波濤終結這腐敗

1386
02:40:27,639 --> 02:40:31,589
The truth has to come out some way and if it has to come out this way then we are all for it
真相必須得到揭露, 如果 非要以這樣的方式, 那我們都會贊同

1387
02:40:31,779 --> 02:40:36,339
If we want to shake the entire population out of their slumber then we need an explosion like this.
要想撼醒全國的人民, 我們就需要這樣的"炸彈"

1388
02:40:36,339 --> 02:40:39,999
We are going to sit and just talk about the thing So we got to do some steps
我們不能總坐著討論這些, 必須付諸行動

1389
02:40:40,039 --> 02:40:43,239
And they have done it, they have taken a right step..
而他們做到了, 他們做了正確的舉動

1390
02:40:43,259 --> 02:40:47,819
When we grow out of this, well be a nation which is beautiful and free of corruption.
等我們從這裏成長起來, 國家會變得美好沒有腐敗

1391
02:40:48,089 --> 02:40:53,749
in minds and hearts, that's not gonna fix up very soon And we'll see that
深深打動了我們的心, 不會很快忘記 我們會讓夢想成為現實

1392
02:40:53,769 --> 02:40:54,419
We will do it
我們會行動起來

1393
02:40:54,539 --> 02:40:58,589
Lord, accept the sacrifices of these children.
神啊, 請接受這些孩子的犧牲

1394
02:41:09,029 --> 02:41:10,499
I come here with Sonia a lot
我經常與Sonia來這

1395
02:41:11,369 --> 02:41:12,339
Just like old times
就像以前一樣

1396
02:41:14,629 --> 02:41:18,139
And sometimes I hear voices carried by the evening breeze
有時我聽見傍晚的微風帶來聲音

1397
02:41:19,279 --> 02:41:21,349
Not words, just sounds
不是說話聲, 只是聲音

1398
02:41:22,509 --> 02:41:23,479
Sounds of laughter
歡笑聲

1399
02:41:47,589 --> 02:41:49,049
Come Bhagat...
過來, Bhagat..

1400
02:41:51,889 --> 02:41:53,879
Dad, what are you doing?
爸爸, 你在幹什麼?

1401
02:41:54,259 --> 02:41:58,219
I'm sowing mango seeds. If I plant one, a thousand will grow.
我在播芒果種, 撒下一顆, 長出成片

1402
02:43:10,979 --> 02:43:16,219
MiG fighter planes have served our country since 1964 and have been instrumental in winning us wars
印度從1964年即開始使用MiG戰鬥機 在戰役中起了相當作用

1403
02:43:16,219 --> 02:43:21,219
However over the 15 years, 206 MiG planes have crashed and 78 pilots have lost their lives
然而15年來, 有206架MiG飛機墜毀, 78名飛行員喪生

1404
02:43:21,219 --> 02:43:26,179
In their memory and in honour of our Air Borne Warriors who have laid down their lives for our country
為紀念這些空中勇士, 紀念他們為祖國獻出了生命


